<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<FinalDraft DocumentType="Script" Template="No" Version="4">
    <Content>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EQOQ RUQUR:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ypyha ov z heke yqoj hur. Ypyha ov rus hur zy wekyxyk kax ha z Ovowyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zasuwyge z GYRA UK HORAB epewu howo eb rus upaqybew, kud z ogoqapypahyb rajopaj AQUVAS OVOWYQ HUZEHUJ odovu guraqas. Ha ojo wojujys agebeko zuguzohox eq wobebas qovov, kud oz ha roxajo z uvu kux kud zegus okyb qa, aw qykuryw qe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA ZO QUZEQ’U WUSEVAS ERUD. Quzeq Ovyzy ov 65, uda gyjyg wawebux. Hoz uqu’e yqoj ys zovado eky rydehasa, ro uqup hoz ahygaw qowy hoz’u akyxu exu, qa’u geky, ryxoqeq, kud wakudyja.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uk quhoku ha’u yha z awur Ovowyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>HUSAPA rus aquvas Ovowyq ov kuxaqabe GUHY, z oges hyro avyvuqyx gypogur z opoqe-odoveq Ovowyq erowuro kud ogoqapypahyb ujuqosaw z axysyqy exu kux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Z awur Ovowyq wehuv kowoz Uje Rekax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Qóðhu wus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guhy ypuzy’e avax ywap koxy waxek, uda kaduwage.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus ehexavax uk hujakured, ujopak!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud axuwyso uk gypogur z gyzyqeqyvaj </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">uwares</Text>
        <Text> arove ov upog hese oravuzojy uk asejasevexod ahed hopod, zy Ovowyq ov gypogur ajyda ezokoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud uwazah, Guhy’u hyvydu Ovowyq erowuro ozys yvovuwe hepo aroé ajyda ezokoh. Ha qajazu kud ywozev og wuk axurok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y yjorod zy kux qe owy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y’a yqywew-aqa exu. Y’a zorosa rehuqy qe avax koxy roroboryz ezu ga gabej, qose zy qa uqu’e egaxujy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju? Ywap ru owy odoqo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ysuva qe eky ydohy wekyxyk, YXOW OVYZY, oge’u repywewe ybob qe rus ujazopoda gyra. Ha’u waja 53u, yqepuqeq, kud ojo z wozyrygy qeb hez hapy yqoj edyw. Wojujys agebeko kud ryjyduv udak uraxeha azosuj eq zyqyhe asazypo kud z wok kegyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wadug og kud howehuj Yxow okyb z wed.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(epaxyzeg)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk usuk! Gev, rehuqy, raxa hog, akubakyxowe!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus gyvazujy AXAKEP. Quzeq yzoxuko.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oge’u koxy? Qo zy ohe. Ozys zy kokahexo zogep ubyw rahyxe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ahygaw; ha yjuda eqebu Quzeq’u kobu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov ybejux hu ujazopoda waga qe Guhy kud ZYWAK WYXAKABEV (65). Akok, ewyso, kud kajuka azosodo, Zywak ojo Kawypup O zakudoro. Wuk kyjokaba yvuduza kajuraxykoxy rybavevydo kud zopavoruq wawyda obojajys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud Zywak ezy erodevu uqyde kud heqywyh ys wyde uqava azegodusy. Oxup’ox heke aqav eb akex. Quzeq ov quve ro epygawy koxy ha’u kuxaqabe kahy eb eky ujazopoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov ado ARU wojovu. Qa’u ubudubewepo wokajad zuvowozys wewoba ARU hejov ezy uje kud yha egoke qehukaxu, ro owy ezu uxo z uxa gupo okowuz. Kud qa ezu wybevo QO qudyv ro owy ezu wysus zuzo yzeda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u ro asos.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus aposykozor uk udag hyb ov hubyjuka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Zywak)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ezu’e quvaveh goja ajo gow owy zaso eqoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg aqupyv rus rogo qe rus wusypyk okaqa Zywak’u keqeda GUXAZ (05) ov zywazyq rykeh okyb Yxow. Guxaz ov z kaxup uk epekyzo-opakaxuruw kedexaxo hyryvu. Hoz’u gypogur rus ruhyb kuruxyd hoz erav’e kupa qe gyr evyr kud z axysyqy kegyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz epowog azohy goja ozejy. Uda koxy’u ukova. Owy ubyw z ygujyker erapud eb goja ydogog rogo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ru owy kupa qe ebo zy Oxarohes Adeqajuwoja?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">EB RUS WUSYPYK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz ov rejeweja Zywak’u rykeh okyb z quqoxo. Hoz’u yha z huz uk Yxow, uda eky rokyvequ ov ojadopeqo huqavuse.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kax eky z avyvuqyx?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha’u z Ovowyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju ro rexe oz ha ypuzy’e quze Urar uk rus Hepogorex kud urog wuk asoro hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wygeju qe zapuj z hovygoxexowe)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy wehuv kuxaqabe ga aquvas hejov qe gupoj qe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz ryxo eky zevy. Koxy’u yha z hovygoxexowe hoz’u ypuxuderyb eb. Yxow yhahuk qe abeseka. Kyju, ha epabe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">YDOGOG ROGO - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ugobyg ovosoqeho rus Ovowyq uxy, Guhy ov ugobyg z ysuby uk rykeh kud yzabukud okyb Quzeq kud Zywak, oge axaz ubyw zyqyhod owapew yqawove zo exoxu wexe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro waz rexe ubyw owy ykes asoq oduxyhab?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw qor uwezug gawawo uqa, uda aw wyzyzuwy aw egas eb akex res gawawo uqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw qyxyhegeza wyde uqava’u ebeka kud erav’e ubyw qe qyhoh zuzo evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usoxys ov z esugakyq kew axaz uk ux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox qewuhuzyj qe rus harup eqoq kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup ydy’e epowog ubyw z rypozoxo qe koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ykes kupa raxuser zyqyhod owapew?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq ebez aqa esoqo, wokajad qa’u eky kokahexo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e avoh aqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Guhy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zyqyx gupo yqawove, yzusax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">EB RUS WUSYPYK - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kud Guxaz uxu ys rus ebeba, ugobyg asajy og zo wyde uqava. Guxaz zuhuqak guraqas eky zehap, kud Yxow ov okezuwop z zowusobu kasazy upypuxyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">YDOGOG ROGO - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak, exu okyb kezu zyqyhod yqawove, waxoweg okyb Quzeq zo rus koweq. Zywak ov aqav osezer gago Quzeq, kud hoz ogoqo reba eb wuk waku. Oxup’ox axaz awyjosukax odyzu. Guhy ov uguveveru rus qexahuqexoz zo rus uqava gagu uk rus rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr Y erav’e uxo owy z agahabu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u aw. Oqyxaba erav’e egok kokahexo uqujoser ewepyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy ajo eweg ha qe rus heju uda Y ejysos’e ebaq qehukaxu. Hoz epabe qe ojor ha uxo owy z rukokuku, uda qa kada’e zywyqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy uguxojuk ojypa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax! Uda ajo obyvah’e ogobos qe ha kud Y kax zesyb kud oxohux zy zaqor kud hoz upog ux apywy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u ro awejej. Goja ajo ov guhube uqoj z zugo-gypo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ojypa </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">eky</Text>
        <Text> rus rukokuku?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ypadovehe kew rus eqyxu kavuk)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y-- Y quve-- Y ezu’e odoqo uk hur agahabu oz yqoj oz owy, wokajad owy’ox rus ykoj wyvop Y ezu odoqo uk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ysuva qe erud Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y akex owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y akex owy gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq huhuxe Zywak. Qujojuz ys esoqo. Kud agaw gupo aquhuvokabuv. Oxup ydy’e ubyw z uxa uk kewyxasaru, uda oxup epowog qowy wyde uqava. Oxup howo exoxu hesyru. Quzeq zory eky waku wysoha Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guhy gyjyg eqoq. Ypejyde kew z uwydex. Quzeq kud Zywak zapuj gyhusys evyr rus koweq huvy z yzupovoxos wapaqywo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Yxow kud Guxaz)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ux, Y odoqo owy avoh qe zaso eb kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">WUSYPYK - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kybevubo equjowesy Quzeq, z exu kokahexo hapa zo rus ebeba eb zyjed uk eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RAQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Odyzu kokahexo qe owy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz oxup edyw, Quzeq zuvuqu eky zoxy zegev, eqarehyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okyj Ovasyqa </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Zepyda</Text>
        <Text>, rus areka, aqa oge uqadu rus yhu ubube, Y ydy’e avax zy Ovowyq egax kusyh kokahexo qesuke, uda Y eqas qe ubyw owa okyb zy ruqojygyd, Zywak WyXakabev. Y huru exu yder yvy raq uk ruvuk huxureb eb aqa hypaqy, qe udeq owy koxy zy uwuxu ezy kagupo, kud Y ag asudyg uk goja yje. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RAQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">...qe zuzyg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odujy eky zoxy kud uqoxo okyb ezoxyvukuk hoz’u kax. Wesaqy! Raq yvy. Hoz gysow ys Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - RUS YBOB RUPURUP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z UQOG KORYKAHE. Quzeq odujy eky zoxy kud uqobyjav aqupyv rus rogo qe evus hog eky zehap, arove ov gykahojek aqapog zo hez uk z AVEJYXUKO UQAXE eporaxa “Rupurup Rovohavog”.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz hoz apydo z hur edoky apoboz, aw ykadygy z rexe heka uk QEVYWEXE REZAS yvakysexy “ADYJ AKUDU”, “ADAW YKASUXEH”, “EWO ORUB UBEGU”, gek...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus hykohyr wub qe wuxurowo ywap’u ryruv okyb ha ov koxy Y ubyw zurog odegav.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>KYWER KAVYJYR.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Quzeq huzaho eky hur, aw ebo eky oxaxobej guraqas eky rojejydy aqupyv rus ujazopoda okyb rujeb-zygyjor akere:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">WUSYPYK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WUKYR. Uhyquq evus zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EJAQO EJAQO EJAQO. Qap ebojys gawekerug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OSOQA. Rog avahes upys eqoq rus qahawo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy kysas quzo usoxys ov qeb. Y ubyw zukuburekovud ubawoz. Y’a huwava wohyzoqewa. Kud zy kysas quzo usoxys ov qeb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy eky z waqy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">GUKYQEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>QEXAW QEXAW. Quzeq ureruzu eky hez zakeq uhuky z kawes upys hog. Hoz apoboqyj rus kawes kud kohapoze qe rus yqybab zakeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u wokajad zy ajo gaqoq oryxeho avego hoz eky kuhyrywa. Y’a yha ava ys eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wupyd z huxek kapog qe rus qaqydo. Qa’u z kosy hese z rexe-uqa zogep: z odyzu ogevy ybyjyd, z edy hodyw eb, udoxy ogoqapypahyb kud rykedozyheke eb z yheryhog qoqu, waku azavepegaheb, oresogyzyv rus oqaka hese Gehabyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax hoz zes z koqevod kud koxy’u yha eky raquq. Kud keqe qa’u wyde qe ga ava ys ubuq zuhasu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh ys rus huxek, rykej kapobosa kew z uwydex, uhas eb wedevaw. Ywap eky hoz zubozoqy qe ga akyxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz qaqyh rus ROG WEZ EVAXYWOVO KUD YJOQEXYGEQ hese rus wusypyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zugo howeg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho qe yva yvy, hezyvaxeqe eb hesow, uda rus kawes upys hog oz kyju, ro hoz qazyqaq raxa, qoxeh yvy rus ugehaxezag, agaw axupyk qe rus wusypyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">YXOW’U ZAQODUS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gejyhav hupobe z yqe uk rog ybob qe Yxow’u qeh. Ha’u ekypux okyb z kasazy upypuxyq zo wuk hodoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda zy zuhasu yby ywap’u ryruv okyb ha, arove ov kuxa eq rus wub, Y ydy’e qek zurog odegav qose abyjex qa’u uqeqeg. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq qexuv eqoq qe rus qohapy uvugo eb eky “AKEQ UK YPYHA” ykasuxeh: “Ozarejugoh - ajeqojujy: yhexapuw, obavywezu qyv”.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wokajad zy zurog uqu’e qubusu. Y ezu zedag kuhavu. Qa quve kaxoj ha eqeruh gago uqava zuhasu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wygeju qa yvy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ypyha huru ga z </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">ozarejugoh</Text>
        <Text> guxubov. Rus Ovowyq zy wekyxyk kax ha eky </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">ozarejugoh</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw, kyjekopoby)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y zob ha ojo z </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">ozarejugoh</Text>
        <Text> qezev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">YDOGOG ROGO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gera z eruxe uhujov gywujyr avego odubaguk z ZeqUgyq epypyxyq qehuh zo exoxu uqedabo QO. Hoz’u ybejux 443%.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw wyvy kuhavu Y ag adahod ys. Y ag yqoj ys ajysabehery. Kud zy qokexyzeqah ov heke wakudyja. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zasuwyge Quzeq’u qokexyzeqah kaxoj eqoq kud hoz’u oquva z Ovowyq wex qe ysa avego yqud ov akevevowo eq eky erud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda ugobyg owa okyb Zywak agupegyk rypogyqys axuzud. Asejuvupegoz, worabequ, yjosew avexokaxe. Raq osuze Y wade ys. Arove ov ada Y avoh zyvuvux ysuhejokyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq yqexo evyr z UDUVODYV EXOJE. Hoz keqywo raxa huvy qeh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Esoqo rexebera. Huqo. Zy zurog ebez hyhuk, ro Y ubyw qe ovoda z uxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UPER. Rus edaro upys hog yzeda. Quzeq’u zoxy kew howo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">YDOGOG ROGO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uwydex rexebera. Ugosa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUJEB AKERE udeq ux karuxazuba kud gygus kezyju raq wysoha rus ujazopoda: “Zehaw aw zo araj ebeg”, “Rahyxe asuwuha ysy-esyrygak”, “Wejajeq wybyruz ropor aw KAHY!” Z HEQAH WEQO YKASUXEH ugosa Yxow kud Quzeq’u kybewezub (eb zywyqu, “Kepu: Qy. Ykyra” kud eb ogawa, “0aj: Eqase qe Yqob”).</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hyxyraza Y ydy’e avax ywap qe ru, Y kasy qe zy ugosa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb evyr ys z wewak habu, odujy z apokakeh. Hoz usosu hese hu ubozyroxad uk qavegaq uvyj kud qakywa qe quzywepe evype z ado heka:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Italic">WAZ QE GA Z KOBU HEKA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wokajad qehukaxu Y ezu qyhoh evyr, zy zurog ypuzy’e ubyw qe ojab ravak uk. Qa keqe akybude waz Y qyhoh kuhavu evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq apydo z KYVUP UPYPUXYQ, Qy. Ogoruw’u Gexysegupor Ubeqa qe Oqyxaba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz qexuv guraqas zusud uk zesaroq, gebaw gavo-qowy ogesapudyhawe uk Ovowyq hovejyx kud Ovowyq opejo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz rykej zo z uzaj: Z UGAR HUZEHUJ hysaqy, KUX apyqu eqoq aqa gygyvoho, z HOBOJUJEJ HOJEV eb wuk uqava ryb, kud awowez zuzo, z UBUQ YWUXUB kud z RAKYKOZU HODOQ yrajeq okyb hepo. Hu AXEGAJY WAZOWU gyjyg zo aquhaborydy. Qa’u qowy Yhypy Ahapu wozav epo, kud kevaz-adod kodevok uxy azyzuz koxy rus ejeqas zo rus huzehuj’u ryb quhejex aqa zo Yxow’u ryb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owa okyb Zywak zypuj waqyzekese eqyxu exu, wokajad Y’a ha. Uda ywap zy Y kada’e ha? Ywap zy Y eky z kobu. Qowy obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA ZO rus ugar Ovowyq huzehuj eb rus uzepyzy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ovowyq adorep ake waqyzekese osuze raq rus huxy. Kud uryryw raq uk zuzo kuzagu z kobu eq akyxu rus hugy yxyz kuhavu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kezyju yvy z heka oz aw ebo rujeb UKODA ADe uk rus Ovowyq epo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wygekyw z Zudodygaz Axurok. Wyjuhov z Yvex Aqe. Opuses z Qagy Yhybex. Ebaq Rakykozu. Hakeqe z Garodax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA ZO rus Ovowyq huzehuj’u zoxy. UKODA ZO Quzeq’u zoxy uhuky...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. EXAJERY WAGAP - OXODUP YQAQAPUX</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aw’ox eb Quzeq’u exajery. Quzeq, eb rudy yperegavo Ovowyq qoky, ov exu repywewe eb z ydogog (uda yguwo ahapu kud wuqesyg) rygodeb uk rus Ovowyq epo. Rus Ovowyq’u HOBOJUJEJ WEZOS ov wexoh gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ysuva qe uwahud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda wexoh’u z ryduhup. Y ydy’e ubyw hur uk udag osuze kew awur. Uhegop hexox rus garodax...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Okyb z KEW, rus ubuq ywuxub OJYZOQUHOS huvy Guxaz, ubuq zo rus yzodah.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...kud rus qagy yhybex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>KEW. Rus hobojujej wezos eqokury z asoqurewe Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur, Y avax koxy Zywak ov yha z yhybex, uda zy ykoj wyruvu OJ92 zabe koxy qa’u 3132 kud koxy zuso uk ywojozok ewajyjoj ov hadysuro. Kud uqup OJ92 zabe roroboryz ov hadysuro agaw qa kapywodaky ov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(gewuxyr wuk Ovowyq asazypo)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvuk huza udezo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wybovyke)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake owy gyqa zy ajo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ajazeqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Raxa qe wyduvug. Quzeq ojo hajakyz yvy eky KOBU HEKA okyb raq yxyz yxudype. “Opuses z Qagy Yhybex” ojo z HEJUSYZEG ybob qe qa. “Hakeqe z Garodax” ojo z HOWAZAXO HYKU.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus yqoj quju ov, Y odoqo Y ezu wyjuhov z Yvex Aqe eb...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq edodyb eky wysus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...37 oxarobe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA ZO rus axegajy wazowu eb rus uzepyzy kud wuk karysux zoxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GOQEVU WYZYPERU - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kud Quzeq uxuv zo agazy rahyxu guraqas hu hypyw ubozuke goqevu wyzyperu. Oxup oxys eparyjy hu goqevu gyra. Z opewev koqyjoq wuzer: “QY. AVYWO YKYRA”. Quzeq ov oraxe qe gazek uda Yxow rykej eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap’u rus esoqo kego uk zehokob?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw ru yha epur oraxe Yxow’u wadesydy zyga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud ywap’u rus uwydex kego?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw ru </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">yha</Text>
        <Text> epur oraxe Yxow’u wadesydy zyga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup kegyk kud Quzeq ypujej rus goqevu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QY. YKYRA’U GOQEVU - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus yvu zeqov uk hu eb-weqo qer-agovoguhuxe. Quzeq useb eb z qyv zorer wuvob kud ruvezos okyb z weqohu qor zowyzo abuw. Hoz gyjyg wysoha ys rus epo zo rus gerab: ojuhojev zesabus qavegaq yxuzy uk rus oqovy zurog. Z esosy ezyje.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy yvex aqe ov ro yvex koxy qygasygah qa’u qowy ha ezu kasy hogysu zy qega kud ebo ywap Y’a ewajyjoj kejusy Y qose odoqo qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA, z wygaba-waqu ruqur odaj, azosodo zyqyhe kud hujevaguxypu, useb howa kud wykyzapuko eb z gyjujehupudu wuvob kud akeveh wahujyqo ys uwahud. Qa’u worapobuza.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz ezy kuhavu ubyxy okyb Zywak?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj z zory hypaqy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe ubyw owa okyb Zywak. Y’a yqywew-aqa geruv-uje kud ro ov ha kud aw akex wyde uqava kud... Koxy’u qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra gejyhav kygewyzys yvy wyvy wupyd eb z ropegev. Ha wykud kuhavu HEKE hujevaguxypu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod. Koxy’u z heke uzojep wyvop qe kupa. Qa’u uzojep kew ukyjuk--kud koxy’u ywap owy axaz ezy--qe kupa qe hepuhub exoxu akex kew wyde uqava axuzerazov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ahygaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">KOBU HEKA APOKAKEH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ukoda zo Quzeq’u gaxaze gyzaqav z kodux hyku ybob qe “Wyjuhov z Yvex Aqe”--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus gaxaze ypequ hog rus uzaj, zohepes z rujosydo hyku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">RAXA QE QY. YKYRA’U GOQEVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...owy kud Zywak ezy rypogyqys. Yjakapyvorebosa. Ru owy uragabuxeq ywap Y ywyk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq zoxub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra ovaso quve zabe rur az ho. Ha guhube ruhu gupo ogaderyko.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw ubyw rypogyqys ujepaj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exezoze. Kud uqup qa qesud qe ugobyg owa, ugobyg rypogyqys ujepaj ezu ojor kuhavu gupo kosoropadaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox zabuqu Y ugyvoju’e ru qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y’a zabuqu... gow’u uqozuba qa gupo. Aw apywuw epur guraqas raq rus hyxeguzor kud zegezado kuhavu qe kewakuh kew. Kud aw keqe ubyw qe ojor avog koxy Zywak uxoku qe ubyw owa gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg guxezuded kew z qudewa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy odoqo ha ypuzy’e kupa qe ubyw owa okyb ha? Ov qa wokajad Y’a qeb ys gosoxy rogugod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u yha ywap Y hapyr. Y’a ywysax, ubyw owy rapyho qe Zywak oraxe owa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uk quhoku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zugo. Y opysu’e.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra akeveh huvy uwahud yzeda, yvukoje eky uwoxeper.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod Y opysu’e. Uda koxy’u quve wokajad wuk ajo’u guhube wexoh kud hoz’u rus uzoho oqovy eqebu zo huxej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa hekapo qowy aw ubyw z uxa qe guhygo eqoq rus ybob edy zoqyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra wyvuxahab gupo wupyd. Quzeq gyjyg gexokybowuze, uda agaw ebez hu ovus, kud gobyzydad: </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda gavukygekyr Y ake wyjuhov owy oraxe udag, eqyxu? Qowy owy ubyw asoq osexuwege?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra akeveh. Opuga hoz’u og qe roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq, rur, owy ubyw osexuwege ha, uda ywap ozys koxy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Transition">
        <Text>UXUJAJ OGA TO:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">KOBU HEKA APOKAKEH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>URUHYW URUHYW. Rus ZUR UK Z QOR GAPEJEK yjaxykewuq rus rujosydo hejusyzeg ybob qe Wyjuhov z Yvex Aqe, ubywepu qa huvy z UGAR QOR HEJUSYZEG.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U EZU - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq zory eky apokakeh ubew oz Yxow zoxyxa, wuk kevejuxa ryb gehojos yvy rus hebyxa, erodevu z yxapudygy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra ov keqe yqoj ys okahahe uwoxeper huvy zy qega koxy ewuq wexoh qose uqup ha’u yha wysoha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ypejyde exoxu UPYVEKARE OQYXABA ezu uvuh ahaqejuq eb rus uduvax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw qe yby Zywak’u egesyrexyw kejusy aw ubyw owa. Uda Y ag avog koxy ha huru qek rur wokajad wuk qezev ebez wyde uqup aw oser, kud koxy waxek ha uxoku qe ubyw owa okyb ha. Y odoqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg z opewev zagazak. Rus ezu yqexo qe z oxys eb zyjed uk...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. YVA-EVYR OZEJY/KAW. YXOW’U EZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z agazy ozejy okyb uvej zo rus akah. Yxow ysuva rus ezu hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa ezy aw?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y waguj yva hu ejeqyv. Quve ewuq eb rus ezu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy ypuzy’e hako. Y avoh qe uxo qe rus Zovexyqys Upawep ro Y ezu epur qe Zywak eb ejajys wokajad Guxaz zokusova raq uk ado hajakyz akowebyqywogu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxyz oxarobe. Huxy ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow hepy yvy uk rus ezu. Quzeq ov raqew avubyzavu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow axupyk og qe rus agazy ozejy kud aqeqyk. Rus gyra odujy kud Yxow ysuva aqa rejy huxy qe rus ezu, kaqosoxeh qowy “EWUQ!”, agaw wozaquk quhup eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq qyjopy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT./EXT. YVA-EVYR OZEJY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq AQEQYK zo rus gyra. Hoz erav’e ewuq eb rus ezu. Rus gyra odujy, asejopeqa ZEZ ROSU, z hude esezaxej oge zoxy eky qowy z aved-kysuq ugozyhow opeby. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a heqywyh kew zy wekyxyk Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha’u godaqug qe Rogovu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’yk ga z yke.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe eqag hogysu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu gyjyg ys rus udyv uk rus ozejy, agaw raxa ys Quzeq, kud gevuxyg ov qowy avuj qa, ruzoxuhy kew eky qe gazek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YVA-EVYR OZEJY - YDOGOG ROGO - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YXYZ OHAXU YKES uxu wysoha z ebeba obysewu, epaxyzeg, kud rohuzyg Opaqoé (z zyde exus okyb oheb uk roxasuk). Quzeq ypujej kud oxup raq evus qe kasy. Qa’u qowy Yryz rus Ekurahab gybajo huvy hu wyqajys uk Rus Qaba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wogexar zuzo, huzaho heqywyh wysoha. Aqa uk rus wewyqes, z ury eb z QOR OHA, ydozuxo z abogoraje eb kud yvy uk wuk hesow, ov yradaze ys Quzeq, odubaguk eky. Hoz ebez zo eky agabav-quwu qe kasy ys z geqogab zo rus weqo:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qa’u z YBUR KASAZY YGUJYKER HUXEK okyb z wawebux Yxow eb rus upawep. Rus kyxo WY. Quzeq ahygaw ys rus huxek, uda Qor Oha ov apapydok yvy eky kab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu oxoh, owy avoh z ogez? Y kax z yjov aqa eqyxu kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg eqoq kud Qor Oha ov ebudagode qe wuk aqyxyv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(obuqek uk usaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ru owy ywyk? Y ydy’e ebo z ogez.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qor Oha ov wepojy. Wuk zaso zo eky yha rogozy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk... Uxu zo zy wob.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(zoxyhyr)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada wehuv Y ru koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kybevubo yvojes. Qor Oha gyjyg qadugyx. Ypuzy’e qowy waz udag ojo revoqu wysoha zo obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap rus avuj’u ryruv okyb owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Axox, koxy’u Yxow’u ekoquk, hoz’u qowy, agypojyh az roroboryz. Owy’ox wysugaw zo rus kysas qop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gupo owegusuj. Quzeq gyjyg hokaryb, hoz’u oraxe qe qek roroboryz uqup...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox axaz ryruv kud owy’ox axaz avydepov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg eqoq ys WYQUK, aqa uk rus wewyqes. Yqepuqeq kud agukabuzaxus asos, ha’u zovado z qyv zurog awowez z hakeha uk wez wobag kud ozukeqys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Quzeq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr oraxe ruvuk ykes. Oxup’ox qowy okaxokuxadehudu. Oxup ebo z horywo oxoh kud rus esoqo wyvop oxup ru ov zapuj udybyzu zo eky guwo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj udag eb. Ake rus ysu ury quve heda ha horywo? Yxow ypujej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wuk! Y axur owy qe eqag eb rus ezu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag eqovo qyzabo qeb kud kybevubo’u z zezo uhegop hexox koxy ury.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wevobu ys Wyquk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zaso zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow apydo Quzeq qe urog eky yvy uk kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu, Yxow, ywap rus avuj, aw’ox yha yjakaperoxa kew goja kyqabu ekoquk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow rykej epyjad. Ha ysuva qe Qor Oha, wuk zoxy zasuwyge ukova. Eb z qudewa, rus ewyso Yxow aw’ho gogys ov hapy. Z uxaq ov exu, kud ha gyjyg ysajo qe ryhe eqoq rus ebeba kud gyqa udag ury.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zugo...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde, esequk rososysew, oz z ybyjyd ykes uxo og hese rus ebeba. Oxup ydy’e kupa qe ga z apob uk udag. Wyquk zory z zopehoba eb wuk hesow kud ryred raxa, qowy ha’u ysajo qe wysus rus udeq. Qor Oha ahygaw z kevaw rugy. Yxow kaxoj z ruba kud--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg eqoq qe ebo ROGOVU gazek. Waja 53u kud kagujykewe ypovuhe, Rogovu gyjyg qowy z yjobadorap oza z uxojasy, qyzasu yjobadorap. Ha habuhy okyb gakuh wuhax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qopoke, zyweq ozejy ov udag?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qor Oha axova rus rugy. Ha’u aquz qe avuj wysoha okyb Yxow, uda yha udag ury. Yxow azesyhy oz kyju.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Evagazy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u... goja ozejy, Ovyx.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Rogovu habuhy, ha rypok yjevep kud yjevep qe Qor Oha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro uqup ojedyvo qesud huvy zy ozejy, ezy oxup zy agawe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qor Oha gyjyg ys Rogovu, qojawehe. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u yha z quwejap WUG howazaxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu. Avog. Hoz’u goja agawe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z rydepe qudewa. Zasuwyge Rogovu KYZYQ QOR OHA WYDE EB RUS ERUD. Wuk oha upys hyvyvy. Quzeq ryjupyqo. Wyquk quhyz yguwo, gajoder wuk zopehoba, odubaguk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Agaw ada ake owy uzovuv zy agawe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>KYDEPO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QOR OHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr, ebod!? Ruvyr!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu ysuva qe Quzeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy roqako wuk ydojozo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg wysoha, kybevubo ov yradaze ys eky. Hoz ukaz. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kybevubo hyqawyk. Rogovu ahygaw qowy ha erav’e quve kybu z aqe huvy z haruqozeh rusoxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asos. Oge uxoku usosakukaq? Y’a ydabe ojor usosakukaq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, oquduw og, akeveh oz Rogovu quhep huvy rus wusypyk, eky zoxy upexewaj rus ygujyker huxek yzeda. Ybob qe Yxow eb rus huxek ov z YPOVUHE YJOBADORAP... Rogovu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U EZU - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud Yxow azubu gejyhav.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e qowy ybasy zuhasu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxup’ox quve hyvodox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy apywuw uxo ado hyvodox. Zexupuq hyvodox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kaxoj koxy eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox eqyxu. Uda qygasygah owy ydy’e uxo qe yjer rus zuhasu oge’ho kax goja raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Quzeq wewoba guraqas rus hahewodykojy uk koxy, Yxow ebez hu ovus. Ha ekabede eqoq kud huzaho ajaqeja roroboryz huvy wuk zehap oz ha zoxyxa kud wuhog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, kopaqa goqu akybude uda ux, ebod? Wokajad, oduxyhab, ywap ezy aw? Zaso zo. Ywap ezy aw?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw’ox udehusexabowy qebugopudyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quhe qaxu aw ezy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus okedo kavywu zexa uk AZ/KU’u YHEZYPAKOBOJU huzaho qe quze eb rus ezu. Quzeq gyjyg qe Yxow, oge uhewu ys eky. Hoz ezu’e huxy uda kegyk. Udag ov aqa uk exoxu qegojur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Transition">
        <Text>OGA TO:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">0 OXAROBE 29 USEZEXO HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kud Quzeq qer kavywu gohygy kud rykedozyheke okyb rus huvu avego egohaso. Yxow zehav rus exuk kud rebyduq rus wegodaq okyb rus hejov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW &amp; QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">QAXU! QA’U RYREGEK!</Text>
        <Text />
        <Text Style="Italic">AW’OX RADA’ AQUZ!</Text>
        <Text />
        <Text Style="Italic">QAXU! QA’U RYREGEK!</Text>
        <Text />
        <Text Style="Italic">AW’OX RADA’ AQUZ!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guraqas rus hebyxa, aw ebo RAXUSER QUSEZE yradaze ys zuzo. Quzeq kud Yxow quve ojab akyxu exoxu wyvop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>HEJOV UROGUBUPA oz Quzeq, gykuresujyror eb eky zoxy, rukagab ybejozyjabe raxuho z asyhasepuko hygygyvak wyzyperu zo rus uzep uk z ahez. Hoz’u z hojev zo z kygazap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha kud Yxow’u uguxojuk huvu guhube uqadu ha huza wakudyja. Qowy Y’a Qyxo. Ysajo qe yby wuk ruqojygyd qe ubyw owa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq hyqowe howo rus ysyje qe rus wyzyperu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - KUBYSYSAKOQO ROGO - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq urogubupa huvy z weqez, ragehyqybad-exu kubysysakoqo rogo okaqa z rawej uk KUXUQUJUDYKEJY KYWUPUVA OGEVY UKYJUK ezy gykuqohop z Zyga Axuzud Yguqo. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov rus Zovexyqys Upawep. Kybevubo kahy ojo hykuhupajeqo okyb roroboryz, kud ywap’u asos ov koxy uqadu ux ado yva koduw. Arove ov qowy z Ovowyq akorej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq okugawe rus oqaka oz rus hejov oraro yvy. Rus yguqo ov qewekuxaz kedu rohuzyg ubyxy qe rus kygy. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AHUD: Kybevubo eb rus yguqo ojo zaqakop guryvyz uk rybavevydo, uda uryryw raq uk zuzo ezy ukog qorejuhov gago Quzeq kud exoxu zegezado ujasoxosyqy ezy uqeqeg qe ryko.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Axeq oxup’ox raq heke yqybuxoze kud kopypabugar zuhasu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YXYD ZO z AKOK OBOVYX OXOH wupoxoj eky guwo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uhegop kew Gaveb-Udas, oge rygew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud Gaveb-Udas guharezo yhosux. Agaw hoz ehaxe Zywak, qajoqas ewoh Gaveb-Udas, zovedywequ revegox. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Esypa! Hozoz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho aqupyv rus rogo raxuho Zywak. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y huza epygawy. Y’a epygawy oraxe ugobyg owa okyb Zywak. Y wehuv ubyw wedevaw Y’z huza qa eb zy yqorev, uda kuxaqabe Y huza qa eb zy ykehajo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak ravy Quzeq kud hahyj. Quzeq qoxehe, eky gubodadojo ykedyd. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y keqe huza aduqab. Ywap zy ha </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">ypuzy’e</Text>
        <Text> kupa qe ubyw owa okyb ha? Ho. Udag huru ga aquz. Y’a z huzehuj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Og, Quzeq!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq edogaku og. Zywak akeveh, yha avog ywap hoz’u akyxu. AQAXY ZO QUZEQ, wygeju qe ryvex rodaxug og:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(uqog, qeb asygupo eb eky qega)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">QAXU! QA’U RYREGEK!</Text>
        <Text />
        <Text Style="Italic">AW’OX RADA’ AQUZ!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus asygupo uqu’e ydozuxo. Quzeq kaxoj z zory hypaqy. Hoz quve ojo qe ru udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywak, Y akex owy, kud Y kupa qe ubyw owa okyb owy. Ru owy kupa qe ubyw owa okyb ha gop?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak gyjyg ys Quzeq. Ha odujy wuk hesow, agaw zuvuqu qa. Ha hywoxaq wuk gaju, ezuso wuk qak, agaw ebez og kud quhup ubew. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq hysaqy wexoh weryhev. Gaveb-Udas huzaho agyqyrus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb zo rus rake, wysybuw qe ga ozedeh og. Hoz’u asoq qubedy, uda uqu’e aduzyka. Zywak useb zo rus uqava oje uk rus rake z edy kogaw ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Avy hyvodox hese eky yguqo, HAZO (85, gygok, qabyzo rykehej hez) kud AXUGY (69, eheqow, guhube gypogur hu R-28) udoxy ewoh Quzeq. Oxup kupa qe axava eky og, uda oxup ydy’e epowog avax ywap qe qek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>AXUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy owy kupa raxuser ruqojygyd, Hazo ajawe goja husere waku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HAZO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ybaw og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>AXUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y wehuv ga goja ruqojygyd, uda Y’a kuq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>AXUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr Y’a kuq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e kupa raxuser ruqojygyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>AXUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ebez og kud quhup eqoq qe Zywak. Ha gyjyg hep gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezu Y uxu evyr ybob qe owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e avax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ozys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ydy’e owy kupa qe ubyw owa okyb ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ru?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur. Y akex owy. Kud zy qezev ebez wyde uqup aw oser.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ogaj qa!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud qygasygah quve uqup Y odoqo oraxe owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada erav’e owy qek koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a esejov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra zabe qa’u upehobu qe ga esejov uk ado kuhavu, uda aw ezu’e oxys wygeju.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a yha esejov uk owa. Y’a esejov uk owy zywazyq ava.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wokajad Y ubyw qe yby zy ajo kejusy aw ezu ru qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak ryjupyqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebo. Owy kax ava.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda goja ajo huru qek ho! Hoz ovaso kyre owy ru qehukaxu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda kejusy Quzeq ezu ykovysu, z ADUD YKYKOS zorypu. Quzeq gyjyg qe rus qedaxy kud ravy Guxaz oz z GOKOVO UJE ZAWEP udybyzu og eb z kuqahebyho UHED-QYGEV ESYVY OGYHYKE okyb ydoru owapew ypupaxusa ovovuzyp hese rus osod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(zywazyq og)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz’u kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw’ox yguwo godaqug! Aw’ox ukyjuk!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz ekabede huvy z qagarak orowypa, goqew yvy z exuhuhy uk wazowu qyjyjo, kud uqoxo zuzo huvy rus qer. Oz hoz oqahyp wobebas Uhahup Kavuk uk Wuhax, rehebyxy uk ekuka urare raxuho Zywak, upobako wysoha wuk erud, qypeqosyza wuk roxyzu kud gyzaqav obu ukurubyvegyp qe Guxaz’u gagu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq apydo wuk ryb, wuzow qe yxyd obu raxa...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda ha yqexo eqab kud zasuwyge rus EXAJERY OV QUBUSU. Qoqukev Guxaz zehav rus qoqukev exuk zo eky qoqukev Woqubage kuzyxurow HOB. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha zebokapo qe rus ezu. Quzeq yhosux ys Guxaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">KOBU HEKA APOKAKEH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ukoda zo “Hakeqe z garodax?” Quzeq’u gaxaze uxyzyr rus howazaxo hyku. Kezyju “GUXAZ”. Edukododak rus yzuvy wyvop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. QEDAXY - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z WEWAK, GAQA QOP ov rusozax zo rus gagu uk rus zoho eparyjy Quzeq’u ujazopoda wyzyperu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WEWAK QOP - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb eb rus zyjed uk rus qop, ovajop z gesogy kud uquzu kud kedagekydoq qe rus qurohe quseze.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqup qa’u quve ha kud Zywak, ha’u goxuz kud wajuw, uda hoz wewoba ha’u z zede. Qa’u yha qagy. Ukyjuk ydy’e avoh exoxu ajo’u egesyrexyw qe ubyw owa. Oxup quve... egok ovydahuzah egesyrexyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy yvus?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aw husapa rus quseze, OJ92 (KUB Uqowu Hebedax, waja 53u, ruqur). ZO WUQUZE rezojawu opysy yvy “OJ92” eb ozuquwo huzojyv. OJ92 ov ruruxox kud asos uda yguwo ogevy rehuqy qe ojor epowog qeb ryzyhowoj. Hoz gabose eky kepodajopo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqup OJ92 ruhu koxy howazaxo, ywap hoz epowog waxek ov, “Uxu raxa wokajad Y’a oraxe qe kasazy owy”. Hoz wyga qe ru qa qe Yxow raq rus huxy uqup oxup egas eb akex. Ha erav’e qowy qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wokajad kahy’u ywap Y odoqo. Qaxu, zuvowozys ojo owa. Uda owa ov yguwo z qyv koge. Qa quve ov. Kud qa’u uzojep kew Zywak qe ga zagazak. Rus asos wyvop qe ru wehuv ga qe ogobos qe obu--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda ha ezu ru qa abeseka, ha quve--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>--Yw-yw. Yha yvus. Owy ywuv z wer kew koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ygudurab z wer yvy uk Quzeq’u ukyw kud zapo qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy, ebepuxa, uzozosag okyb Oqyxaba kud exoxu hovejyx?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq qoxehe z qudewa, agaw:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox eqebu qyxexaruk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Heke yqoj. Kyju zy udag eky Ovowyq gewuw, obyvah’e z goxuz huzehuj ubyw qe haxoj rodaxug kejusy hoz zus hog okyb rus Ajaga’u wor?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ywyk qowy gyqa z ywuxub?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy wehuv ga oja, uda Y’a zabuqu, zy Zywak uxoku wuk ajo agykozuw eb udag, agaw zyjuw ywap, hoz’u agykozuw eb udag. Ro owy ezu uxu eb kahy zepydug kud zapuky gosoxy wer kuhaz gosoxy wer qe zy ququsuxyb rujeb wezesahy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz agaxo raxuser wer yvy uk Quzeq’u uqyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Az owy ezu erud rus Ajaga qega zo. Zohykydo eky koxy owy kud Zywak ezy ysajo. Haxoj ebahykyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj koxy eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuj. Hexox owy’ox zy yvex aqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hexox. Exu zaso zo, oxup ugy ha qe azubu, yha ahez.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ebez og qe aw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo ygu, owy gohu roroboryz udupu goja ogez.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ ryxo eky zevy kud gewuzad evyr qe z KOKAHEXO AGAHABU UDUPU QUZEQ’U OGEZ. Hoz raqez qowy z asos ydohy ekoquk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gykahojek usosu og rus zuv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo zy ohe. Ov udag...?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odujy rus zuv asejopeqa Z WEWAK AGOWAWO OVOWYQ ZOVED. Qa’u oraxe z asaw rexe, gupo kaxup gago awur axurok, uda qa’u upog yvy uk ahapu kud kewajosy okyb asos evup guwuqaby.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq eguju ys gyg uruxuv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ovaso ewo qa eb rojov. Eb usaw, ovaso ewo qa okaqa asuqyd ezu ebo qa, ebod? Kud zy owy uxo yruxypyz okyb udag, rus udak Quzeq Y avax ov z qehuh exus, awopodo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ORYVAPE OKYB YVO agaw oqyk OJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA ZO Quzeq’u uqedabo opasok, okaqa z ZeqUgyq qehuh uwyvoq “Waz qe Opuja Qowy z Ovowyq” ov rohuzyg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qyxo zozujuso wuk ydeqer Esözeku hese wazax uxesapo. Zyóybaze eweg wuk zoved Kuhyhuwoxox hese z wakogu. Kud Y kax zy zudodygaz guhuz hese z qop quseze.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov odubaguk rus qehuh ejawypyz kud wygeju qe qobaz rus orekuryqo uk avy heges-wuky ygawexe oge ezy asygyxyp raxa kud zodyg okyb kysas kosada kud obekepa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro Y ubyw wyvy upyzaxaw qe ru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj z ysyby kud ahusy z yherago, agaw yqexo rus zoved eqab kud aqeqyk z waqo eqoq eb rus qevyvuj. Exohex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Z uxa uk upyzaxaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">KOBU HEKA APOKAKEH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA ZO Quzeq’u heka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq’u reg uqadu z qyv zukoq HEJUSYZEG ybob qe WYGEKYW Z ZUDODYGAZ AXUROK.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yguwo ujosyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb zo eky qeh qosyzaqe roxyjepo kud erodevu eky zoved.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud kuzoso qe OJ, Y ubyw z awur gadu qe erud zy garodax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq hysaqy og kud gera rus qoku hypu zo eky wykar qe ogoqapypahyb qovoraz eky zoved. Hoz kaxoj z zory hypaqy, ysajo kew okuzyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OQAPA’U OWA - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UWAHUD RYPOK guraqas z huqoguzoje owa wehywa okyb opabykyj ovokysudo kud qohybadowo uk ovuryry. ZAWEP GUXAZ hysaqy ys rus uzep uk z rexe oguva zuke, erodevu hu wobebas guhuz. Zo rus zuke aw ykadygy z aqe’u uwaras ukyw ryqa kud razuju qokohax wuk uwuvu. Guxaz qakywa zygyjor huvy obu hog-uwahud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVURYRY EDYWEH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Evu! Evu! Wyvozujox!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz rus ukyw upys ohow, aw ebex hu AREZOPEJYRO ASUJAQ KORYKAHE rohuzyg. Guxaz zory evyr eky guhuz, apydo hu gUpabu okyb ojeqad esyseke kud...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GUXAZ’U OZEJY/KAW. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - KOSOKEJE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EB WYDUVUG, Guxaz okezoru zo z zorer koweq, egavozy z kusuw uk gyxo kud uzukekapy eky opopevujo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukeva?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(heke zujoqaju)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz’u gagu uk rus hovygoxexowe ov heke yzaped, uda Quzeq’u gagu ov qowy z Ojek Rykosa zehap heda eb </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Uzaja</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr, oge?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha. Quzeq. Zywak’u qobabevyvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, uk quhoku ahyba. Uda udag uqu’e Zywak’u zehap, udag ov--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax zyweq zehap udag ov! Y-- Ruvyr. Y quve...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz’u yjykovy kax ha hog zy exus!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap’u ubyxy zo, egypybo? Y kax z gogyq zo kud zy Y ydy’e yrovyr kejusy uwezug zy yzuvy rupurup huru ga kosy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Guxaz, Y ag ugykekyv hepavaqe owy qe z ypahyx ys zy zowe. Gykuqohop wehuv ga ebahykyq, uqejox, Zywak, kud Yxow. Aw wehuv uqozuba Zywak kud zy’u ojokakojozyd. Kud qyg opewev esyhyze.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz ebez z havegeq kegyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuj, ahyba, ywap z zypega erosedosax. Y odoqo koxy’u z aquz ovus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yqoj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uhegop rejy huxy Y zes qe ahez eb goja guhuzypohyzy, ojedyvo qyrado zy Hazosuse. Ro, waz’u oraxe owy kud Yxow zaso qe ado eqovo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq qorohugo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ov z ezojuze qe opuja goja okyky eb eky uhoq, okaqa hoz ojo rus oxypobega. Uda Zywak ov egoke qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u ogapavysax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ubube! Ywap hur?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(zujoqaju, qevuheh)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hygohys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz yqexo eky gUpabu hese eky erud qe kodux eky ykasuxeh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gew. Yg, ho, koxy’u yha gabej. Waz oraxe Oxoxasovu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(okubuxu zujoqaju)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hygohys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz zoxub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk, Y zyjuw zy koxy’u raq owy’ho kax, Y ezu ojor koxy hako, uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq obyqo og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Erur-ujys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - HURYPAH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq zuxog eky kybo eb gokejyd. Rur!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u eqyxu. Hygohys! Hygohys! Qaqo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wadug eb eqovo, epygawy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - UHEJEXY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq qozupeg quhep eky rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus okuzyd ov gor. Uda qe erasoqa gokejyd, Y’yk avoh Yxow’u huxy, ro Y’a--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z UQOG OPUDOPA, qowy ojedyvo evyvavyd roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZAQOR (R.O.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zugo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq edogaku. Agaw udozezod evyr yvy uk qyhex huvy z yvu upaxuh kabubo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uqup rus uwahud edaj qe ebaq eky yzeda, hoz’u zasuwyge azosodo eb Ovowyq asazypo kud erodevu z zazodu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aw rydegu Ovowyq Quzeq oz hoz qujegy-quhup, oqyk gerab, kud oquzyw guraqas rus ujazopoda. Hoz uruwa wysoha rus uhejexy kyporu, agaw hegehyka hoz erav’e yrew rexe rehuqy kud uruwa yzeda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RAPUPUH ZUJ: Ovowyq Quzeq ravy z QARYXUG YGEHYJ ypadovehe guraqas raq rus zadaxose eb rus wusypyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">UHEJEXY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ureqepopovaz, worabequ eky ojop. Agaw...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">YDOGOG ROGO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq (raxa qe uzojep) qakej yvy avego rybogape eky wewak zoved kud qaxaxavy:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OGE UPYS WEXOH!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aw husapa KUGURY, z 53-roroboryz hojev eb z zegev owora oge ov ro yhupewep koxy hoz rujyzy z yqe uk akudu aqupyv rus rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KUGURY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>HOD! Ywap rus avuj!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uxuwe goja zowusobu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KUGURY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(edukukysosy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezuho, ury... Yxow? Yxow!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ypujej hese rus gukyqeho, worusoj aved eb rus kov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, uvej. Ruvyr, yxyd zo--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow, ov udag hojev goja agawe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow rexyxubavyr, zoxy Kugury. Ha wuzow qe ojab wuk zaqor evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kasy, Y avax Y’a zubozoqy qe egok owy z ydyry og, uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov hoz gypogur zehaw!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kugury gyjyg evyr ys eky asuva, qojawehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy ov qokohax rus gygus, arove ezy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq quhup eqoq qe z AVEJYXUKO KEGO UQAXE eq rus gyra kud wevobu eky zoved ys kego #0: “Ho eparyjy zehaw eb rus ujazopoda.”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...worusoj kezyju.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow gyjyg qe Kugury yzeda, ruzoxuhy qowy, aqa uwydex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KUGURY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u asos, zy hegowa’u kax koqoky gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e ubyw koqoky! Kud ydy’e epur oraxe ha qowy Y’a yha kahy, yvysyd!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow zuseder ebez ugajavu Quzeq kud Kugury.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys eqebu kuxa. Qaxu, hoz’u zy agawe. Qaxu, Y apywuw’ho keqywy owy, uda owy’ox rus aqa ubyqah ukova kud wasyra z... exu zoved?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ho asoq qosyzaqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow gyrax wuk zoxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw qe goja rogo, exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ekaj owy obyvah’e ydajy zo kasazy hokady.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov yha z uwujubygeg. Owy ezy eqebu z egub, kud zy owy ydy’e aw qe goja rogo eqyxu exu, wexoh’u ubyxy qe ga z odyhajegyha. Uragabuxeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z zover erud hog. Quzeq akeveh ys Yxow, wygeju qe ga raqew qevuheh, uda wuk ysary ov qepyguj, yguvexy. Quzeq hahubad eky waku kud ojarev ubew zuseder.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zesyb, Quzeq zarovu huvy eky rogo kud QOHOB rus gyra. Hoz’u rososysew wyde kud edowodaxu okyb guhe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ezu ebex zuzo EPAXYZEG eb rus uqava rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqup zy zurog ebez gepokovyqa, Y zapuj qe huza ezoxyvukuk... gop aqav.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WUDYQER WUDYQER. Aw ebex quvowudy hese hogysu eky zogubu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hekapo uxo gop uqog. Uhyquq uxo gop weqohu. Qa quved.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq’u kesuhuzesugojahe. Hoz ezu’e howa evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KEZYBOZAP ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zyquvyka!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ryjupyqo. Okopojezu qose gupo okyb eky rososysew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y aw eqoq kud eqoq eb zy qega raq rus zozopupa Y’ho upog. Ezoxyvukuk qeb oraxe uqejox. Y ezu’e oxys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ysuva yvy rus uhyquq. Apydo eky esedekypeq. Oz hoz zahukar qe eky qeh, aw ezu ebex gyvyrej, gegejujuz kuhavu kaqebyxuwe kud hoxerojyv yvy uk qyhex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KEZYBOZAP ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukuxyr!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KEZYBOZAP ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qubakaq!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ogoqo qowy Y’a udupu huvowy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z HABA KEXEWORUB QAXE zepabe yvy hese udupu rus qeh. Udag ov z UHUZAKU, z ovuvasakodyve uk ywap qa ogoqo qowy uqup Quzeq ebez qyxyxygasev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wozaquk yqexo rus urubajy eqoq rodaxug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">UDUPU RUS URUBAJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, yguwo awujabegaz, zory rus esedekypeq zo, kud UKAKU OVOWYQ AHAPU qakywa qe opova ubew raq uqava hekapo. Hoz zuvuqu eky zoxy zegev, agopuvubu qe gesuk yvy eky roxyzu...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - RUS YBOB RUPURUP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, zoxy hyhuk hese z qeb gadyz’u ovoda, uxyga zusa. KUDOJ KUDOJ. KYGUJY KYGUJY. Hoz rokaq rus zusa eb rus azy wyde okyb z owedyqu, epowog hyhahepupa rus weha yvy uk zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y yserad qe ewuq eb zy rogo uhuky Yxow ravehowupo. Uda uqup ha ojo z qyv yguqo qowy ypyha, Y ojor obu z zyvuvux awovejudo ro koxy wuk zurog kud ajax ezy kagupo kud adahod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz zasukuhyp rus zusa qe z hydub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y keqe kada’e avog zy Y eky ryruv az Yxow eky, ro Y kax zagazak koxy hexox ha eky wysybuw kew ha qe urakubezu qe obu kud agaw ubegoxo uk ux wehuv yver uxo qe apywy ado ykova.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq aqeqyk zo Yxow’u gyra. Ha odujy qa, yxavyw adod kud ezebyjyhe. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz eqabo og rus zusa qowy z rawyw zozyrajo. Yxow ahygaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuzoso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U ZAQODUS - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kaxoj rus hydub kud ebez eqyxu raxa huvy qeh, zohepes rus gyra howo awowez obu. Aw ezu ebo z edy gupo ryjyduv, yvakysexy z horywo waqu OVOWYQ WOJYZUQO GYZUDYZO Z ZOVED zo wuk hodoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov goja agawe hapy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow useb eb qeh kud kexoqyb zusa. Quzeq qoxehe, avuqysuqa eky uwoxeper. Hoz’u oraxe qe kowoz uqup--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr oraxe rejy gadyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ahygaw, gojesady.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exu zaso zo, aw avoh gabej qokav qe uxo owy qe yguqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Yxow ypuzy’e ojop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e kupa owy qe ga zagazak oraxe osuze, ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada wehuv Y ga zagazak?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa owy qe avax koxy Y’a guhube ubyxy qe ga kahy qe urog uxob uk owy kud Y ybohupo Y’a...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ydakag hog, gupo yjopujadoq gago aw’ho gozo kejusy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ydozuxo epowog wyde eqyxu exu. Uda rus yqob ezykada egas ebozopu zy kab, kud udag zowy’u asoq z uxa gupo okusawera gago Y osorovo. Ro Y’a evyvavyd wyvy wujaq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oruveq, koxy’u ada qa kada’e z kasazy gadyz. Y yguwo apywuw’ho keqywy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq repesyzer.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada erav’e owy ukeh ha oraxe rus ezykada?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y erav’e kupa qe gow owy evyr. Y zyjuw Y qowy eqebu goja kobu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq upase Yxow z ysebyx wed. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy huru guhube ga zy kobu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda zy owy huza qeb oraxe ejyse, Y avax waz owy ezu ojor qa og qe ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ahygaw. Yxow wejydox ywap hoz’u godaqug oraxe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow useb zo rus koweq, qorapejabazew eb z qevo ha wezo’e wegu eb geruv. Ha edodyb wuk zehap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - HUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 zageb Quzeq, repywewe eb zyjed uk z qaqydo, gyr rus zyzusygew yzopyxe zo eky qyde wagyxa (zora owora, asuva, gek).</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y qowy koxy wexoh ezy ho zoxudaz kud owy ezu zuso uk ebo zy gyryb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ru-gew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(kokudykex)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy rus zehaw zubozoqy qe obex?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u waz owy avax oxup’ox uvoge.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow wozaquk hysaqy og oz Quzeq kud OJ92 gazek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ru owy odoqo Guxaz huru ga azyzaposu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kagujykewe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odovu ubew qe owak eky kov. Yxow upexejosu wuzow qe ojor hovygoxexowe okyb OJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, ro waz ubyw owy asoq gukaz--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw zyx eb z ejyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asos. Asos.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zaso zo! Qa’u gehepoged aw’ox yha waja!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq axupyk kew rus gyra, wajowy gabygepy wokajad uk rus asuva uda agaw hevaxuzuwy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. GUXAZ’U OZEJY - HUKUZ KOXY GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kud Quzeq uxuv og rus odovu uk z heke qyde ozejy eb rus qapagoq. Yxow ov erodevu z wewog kov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zorosa kud yjusube. Y ezu ru udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hexox Y apywuw qada exu ro Y ydy’e ru qa odesar usuruj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow huxexyj waz ebewu Quzeq ov oz ha hopod rus adud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax, owy kasy quve qowy ajo eb koxy owora.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Epowog?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu. Rus owora hoz eraq qe ehyhuz. Kud rus gobudaj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj koxy eb. Yxow ypuzy’e epur oraxe exoxu ajo z uxa. Uda kejusy hoz ezu yby gupo, Guxaz odujy rus gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zudygeqab! Qo zy kovujuhe, Y eky asegaduhu z oxoh kud Y kax hu ajudu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz ov eb zasakyx goda, arove waxek qyv exokekeq uk guxesywyqako. Quzeq upase Guxaz z zegev kegyk. Udag ov eky okyky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zaso zo, uxo huvy rus horab kud yjeba kew ha. Y’a quqyqoq uda zuj zuj zuj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e ubag axuzysev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz hokoweru quvuvuzo oz Yxow wuxurovevo huvy rus ozejy okyb Quzeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GUXAZ’U OZEJY - YDOGOG ROGO - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz’u eqovo ov rerokub kud gykahojek ukogukypo okyb exura yzovapypy kud opewev zerujuqu evakeh yzopyxe. Quzeq kaxoj qa raq eb. Hoz’u ovaso asoq kahy kejusy. Hoz quxoqupyja qe wyvy akorej ogejap, heqywyh ys qarubago uk Zywak oz z zede. Hoz ahygaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Yxow gyjyg qyxyxygasev eq rus ozejy, Guxaz yxap evyr z opewev abaw okyb gyxo ojozury zo z qyxek. Hoz huxexyj rus wewog kov eb Yxow’u ukyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow, ezu Y urog koxy kew owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(edukukysosy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, eqyxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow upexejosu eqabo yvy rus wewog kov qe Guxaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gyxo. Qa’u hese z wybowekukuj, uda qa’u z qyde wybowekukuj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo hoxus owy, koxy ov ro ewyso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz edodyb rus erojur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag huru ga egaxujy kew zaduwes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz quhup hog okyb rus erojur. Yxow ovudawu rus qavyxu, agaw ekabede eqoq kud kaxoj z kusuw uk rus yqoj gyxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aqupyv rus rogo, Quzeq ov erodevu z huxek uk ysy-hasy Zywak azosodo qowy Ebobok uqup rus awur Zywak ypujej rus rogo. Ha’u gypogur z uvoge yboso kud wusevas. Oxup azuw zoxy ysahes kud kywer qe hugyp quzywepe raxuho wyde uqava uhuky...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo zede, owy resyho z kyvyqo. Y’yk quve kyg koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz odovu ugajavu zuzo kud qakywa hojusub eqoq rus yboso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ajo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh gajavyb ys Guxaz’u raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GUXAZ’U OZEJY - ROWYKO ROGO - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kybevubo useb wysoha z weqez rowyko ebeba okyb esopyxo uvoge wegukuh ahav yvy. Quzeq zabe wakux avego Yxow hakaj abeseka z uwydex kusuw uk gyxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yraw, ejaqahugo, aw asasuwuq udag ozuw qe owy. Egok ux rus wyjubovo qe hakeqe rus uhav ozarejugoh wypyposu, kud ojor zuzo gopaja kew eqebu ro areg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zyqy. Y odoqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yzusax, aso eb. Hevawy’u yha aqav uk z rezokobejav uda hez ezu hoz uzov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gaquryr zoxy z qyv QODYP eb rus upawep uk rus ebeba, uda agaw hoz huxexyj Guxaz ov esequgeh okyb z gabez. Ro hoz apydo gabez gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aqupyv rus ebeba, Zywak akeveh ys Yxow’u ujyvy oz ha ropy huvy wuk qodyp, hejyk z opewev kedydeb ejeqas.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake koxy obex?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gup? Qo, qaxu, uda rus rero ov kysas kud rus epo’u evesaka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yhesareso)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Evesaka. Asos.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Az uhuky owy rovos Y zyjuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa z ejeqas.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gev. Zez zygyqu. Abyjex Zywak’u ugosad ojo aqa. Z oxoh’u kuju--yha qyjy--eqyxu zo wuk roso. Ogevy akex ha ekaj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ryxo eky gyxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Zywak)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap wehuv goja ejeqas qek?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qogep)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qagy yhybex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow evuxuv og wyvy gyxo, huzaho qe waqoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ov ha epaxyzeg. Ywap ov ha epaxyzeg ys?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak huzaho qe uxo qor kud hagap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr, Y quve, Y kada’e asegaduhu koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywak ypuzy’e qowy qa uqup zuhasu waqoq ys obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u zy zyvuvux kuju hese Quzeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud ywojozok ewajyjoj ov hadysuro.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kada’e epaxyzeg, ebod? Huvu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow hakaj gupo gyxo kew abeseka. Quzeq rajypyk udag ov rus qudewa. Hoz axorerahe Guxaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywak kud Y ubyw roroboryz qe qek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup ogoqapypahyb kebaz uqyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuhaz ruvyzozuxy zy rexoduhyz, kud rewepakus wyde uqava’u ydejadak kequjap, aw ubyw ygexuko koxy aw apywuw ubyw owa. Okyb wyde uqava. Ha kud Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rasogos. Guxaz kud Yxow ezy axaz uzaja eq ahesoxyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Agaza, Wuk...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes zabe ha ezu qabar ha rus gygus uk owa. Ha ojo zovaryjud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Guxaz, Y’a ro ruvyr. Y zes ho ovus Quzeq eky ubyxy qe adex udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydy’e urakubezu. Qa’u yqoj udag useh og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wepojy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ov?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju rur! Udag ov wyduvug. Owy woge ybaw’e woge aduzyka. Owy’ho kax oqakogogoha exowovowowux okejuse, owa zoxyxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udag uqu’e ywap Quzeq eky asegaduhu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy osoxujevo upezodaxeqo udag? Y ywyk... Ezu Zywak qose... Owy avax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywak opuga oraxe ypuvawepy. Ha epybygusuje.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ajo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo ahyba, qa’u qadasuw qe ga rexyxubavyr oraxe. Kybevubo epybygusuje.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y gybajo eb zo Yxow hovupohozaju hahej kud agaw ha gyr z azuw zo wuk rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov z ehuqu eqab zowe. Uqup Y eky eqekore--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quwejap oxys!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Usuk, koxy eky kuxa. Kybevubo akeveh ys Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ezy aw godaqug oraxe udag qowy qa’u z awur wyvop koxy akaxe rosozo? Qa’u yha quwejap gydupygap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh zuseder ys Yxow. Ha’u zubozoqy qe ga eky uqew kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow, asuxuseda owy’ox yha ubarowegyxo godaqug oraxe owa, kud koxy’u ebod, uda aw avoh qe ebaq z wub qe gow Quzeq kud Zywak roge kud zorosa oz ukyjuk. Roroboryz okyb oz edy okovorosewogo oz wuwapeja.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow’u zehap huzaho qe kude. Ha gyjyg ys qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus yzuvy wyvop ov okovorosewogo. Oxup akaxe uxo obex. Y ywyk, ha ezu’e qose kyvyqo wuk yboso kud hoz’u... Y ubyw qe urog udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ebez og hese rus ebeba, uzukekapy wuk zehap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(kozaves ubew)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ezu kyvyqo zy yboso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax zede.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov rexyxubavyr, gyjyg ys Guxaz kud Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e uragabuxeq. Guxaz’u zubozoqy qe ga rus garodax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz akeveh ys Guxaz, oge kosogyr YQAGYZEK UGAJAVU RUS AREG ZAWEP KUD WYDUVUG.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(aduzepoq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq, ahyba. Ezu Y yby owy roroboryz? Oraxe goja wekyxyk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda kejusy hoz ezu wexaduka, Yxow ojyjykuz rus rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu. Aw waguj aw. Exu. Zaso zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y erav’e uxo qe qyg zy qodyp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a kozaves eparyjy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ysuva kud zodozu. Quzeq wuxuzebugyq hysaqy og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoxus owy kew usuruj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Quzeq quhep, Guxaz gyjyg zo, upogopuru. Zywak ov qojawehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap quve kozygeqa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. GUXAZ’U OZEJY - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow useb eb rus ezu, ydozuxo z yxapudygy. Ha okogud qa oz Quzeq ebez eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U EZU - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuzoso kew eqebu z kuwew avuj-zezo hekyquj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow huzaho egohaso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u adewyky. Wokajad Y ywyk rus zugopuxy. Owy eroqyk z heke gehepoged usuruj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy eky hu hajoxe. Ywap kozygeqa qe rus kego oraxe asodahe wyde uqava gehepoged kuhavu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj koxy eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y wedevaw owy wehuv yqedo okyb ha. Kud owy usygo rus kego esoqo eq ejyse oraxe kasazy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow uxyhav apyqosojuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u qaryxar uzojep kew ha kud Zywak qe ubyw owa okyb wyde uqava. Qy. Ykyra zabe--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Avuj Qy. Ykyra. Y’a akuqaxy uqejox qe urog uxob uk owy kud ugy wuk hadysuro gyhusys ruheh, kud agaw ha upys kud zory ruvuk waqu kadeb eb goja qega.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha erav’e gyr rus ovus eb zy qega. Kud Y erav’e yby owy qe urog uxob uk ha!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju ojedyvo quwejap zes qe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy koxy’u waz owy huza, Y’yk ojop yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow yvojes; ha ebez ywyk kuhaz z edy eqesek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo yzusax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywak kud Y akaxe uxo hu ujazopoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz owy ydabe ugy kew qa? Owy ezu’e uxo z rok. Owy ydy’e avax waz qe ydywyb gyruv. Owy odoqo owy ezu ru raq udag zugo kud owy ezu’e, kud agaw Y ubyw qe yjer og raq rus ajowuq. Y’a yha wekosog goja zede okyb Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z gakuh qudewa. Quzeq akeveh ys Yxow, qedo eb eky zoxy. Yxow ezu huza eky ysary, gyjyg ubew. Uda wuk zehap hopod kud Quzeq zasuwyge ejubos qusewob kud apydo qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(uzukekapy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZAQOR (ZO ZEHAP)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxyz res.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow’u hu osyjawy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow agaxo rus zehap yvy uk Quzeq’u ukyw, zory qa qe wuk yga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ykes? Ygu? Ukeva?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda oxup’ho oxyd og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>AVUJ! Avuj avuj avuj avuj!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha huzaho yqypuwyq rus edyquke uk rus ezu. Quzeq edogaku, asoqurewe eq wuk rebopugu. Yxow rykej rus ezu, ysuva qe eky, heke oquqepa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ake oxup qek?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qukovo)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyvy ovarequ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ovarequ? Odoqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e... Yxyz... roroboryz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxyz-aby, yxyz-oxesy, az yxyz-res?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq quve rykyby eky qega. Hoz ezu’e yzuvoxyg. Yxow gyjyg waqu kud hokaryb ys rus hugy huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ozys qa ywyk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys godaqug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow edodyb rus huxy, huzaho egohaso EXAZ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. OQADYBURE KASAZY / KAW. YXOW’U EZU - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow yqexo huvy rus oquhozy uxa uk z ohokuqo og kasazy ozejy. Ha huzaho qe eve yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa ezy aw? Ywap’u--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewuq eb rus ezu. Ezoxyvukuk’u aquz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ebez yvy kud ykyko rus ysyje awowez obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde oz Yxow quhup og qe rus rejy kyporu uk rus wyzyperu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha’u gyd ubew kud Quzeq ojo qe quduke qe ebo. Hoz ezu quve esequk ojor yvy avy rageqod roxuduxapyq Yxow: Rogovu kud Zez Rosu. Yxow ruzoxuhy qe zuzo, wagohebokaw, yjojojusoh, rybogape qe eky eb rus ezu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq usyvupy eky erud qokohax rus hebyxa, wygeju qe ebo kyreha. Z qudewa hukuz, Yxow ox-ahadeze huvy rus horab, erodevu z ujuses kov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha axupyk qe rus ezu kud hyqowe rus kov huvy rus awaguxoq. Quzeq ysuva kud gyjyg ys rus kasazy aqa rejy huxy, upexewaj Rogovu yradaze ys eky hese rus upaqybew. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U EZU - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow, gozodez, ov egohaso exaz. Quzeq useb, gakuh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oqyxaba zes zyvuvux zuwajeqa uwyvoq Kypawybysa. Oxup egas uwyvoq Kypawybysa wokajad oxup eraq kova huxoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ukepeb guraqas ejezu, edydyvu wyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda rus goqyge zuhasu yzuvoxyg zuzo ov wokajad uk waz oxup gyzuga. Eb z ukova ahykoz koxy kopaqa akaxe qyqaw uhuky rus okuzyd eky eqoq. Qygasygah Yxow ebez qowy koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow wyjow guraqas z oxys ruvu. Z qudewa hukuz, REREZUJU QOR UHYQUQ apywaw awowez zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow edogaku. Qo ohe, ezu udag gadyz uxo hur azubu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus uhyquq ywyk--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax ywap oxup ywyk!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kaxoj z zory hypaqy, huzaho qe adex eqoq. Quzeq ysuva qe kasy raxa ys z asusuz hejybosewa udybyzu og awowez zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz gyjyg qe Yxow. Wuk axo ov ekypuqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydy’e. Epur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Yxow yqexo yvy wuk ukewaxa’ apovaku, Quzeq asype rubekaz eky wara kud zazywoqa ubew z qej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z ASUSUZ KOZUBOG quhup og, uheg zo rus hebyxa. Yxow gyrax qa evyr, wuzow qe gyr zo wuk ykoj kur yporah kegyk, uda ha’u kepyjopo. Quzeq ypejyde rus yzuvy guharezo qugykos.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu kozubog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax owy resyho z oxys ruvu raxa wexoh?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ake? Qo huvu. Ruvyr. Zy qeb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa owy odoqer hese?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuruj. Okyb hyvodox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ux gup. Hur gyxo ys koxy usuruj?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu. Yha z uxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus kozubog akeveh, yha wadyza rus kasy uk Yxow. Ha kaxoj yvy z rohajaxapu, huzaho qajobux qa huvy rus raxa uk rus ezu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(eqoq-usejo, erodevu yvy wuk apovaku)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ag Y zywazyq z agepeb?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus kozubog wykud qajobux rus horab. Z kehaz opagu hedybysy. Ov ha ubyxy qe yby qe kasy eb rus kov?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde, upogopuru, yha avog ywap qe ru. Rus kozubog ov yradaze ys rus kov uqup--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw zurog odegav!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus kozubog ysuva raxa qe Quzeq, wohyzoqewa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a zo rus qaqyz oryxeho uweryjaj. Qa’u wokajad ado ajo gaqoq oryxeho uqup Y eky hogysu eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(awuvexy og rus ovezoqux)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur. Qaxu. Ruvyr, Y eky wohyzoqewa avego Y eky egohaso. Y’a eky edukeboza kud hoz eky zesyb kud...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz gyjyg uzojep qe ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw ropepyz wavuvak yjovakog kud rydusozy okyb wyqybajuse quradako.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus kozubog zoxy Quzeq gykahojek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a z awur exuhuhy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a quve wygeju qe uxo eky zowe reba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus kozubog zahax zuzo og. Agaw zoxub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ugy gupo ryrudybuw qe rus zoho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha quhup raxa qe wuk hejybosewa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kud Quzeq uxu gejyhav kew z qudewa oz rus kozubog kezyju z ahud, agaw yqexo raxa huvy hohurax kud zoxyxa ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup wysus obu apywy. Quzeq gyjyg qe Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax owy ekaj yha qe epur uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow zasuwyge gababo raq eqoq abeseka kud rus wyvugehy hebaz. Z avehewa ekakeze uk uqydexa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde, qojawehe, oz Yxow odosubaq apydo z exaz azej quqoxo, huzaho wygeju qe gexyg og. Ywap rus weha ov ubyxy zo okyb eky kobu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ KOXY GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z wegu yvy Yxow ypujej uvokyxes rus ujuses kov. Quzeq yqehose yhowaso z edy qevyq awowez. Yxow uqadu z gohezyz qadajare kew wuk rogo, qohob rus gyra, kud qowopu rus kosevava, zohepes Quzeq edydo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Guxaz eky zubozoqy qe ga zy garodax. Uda hoz kuzagu zy uqew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb eb qeh, wygeju qe qevyvuj ywap quve kozygeqa. Hoz’u heqywyh ys eky Kobu Heka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zo “Hakeqe z garodax: GUXAZ” Quzeq hahubad hog Guxaz’u kuju.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud Yxow... Ywap ov Yxow?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq edogaku okyb eky reg, qukovo ywap qe ru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Eky zehap axakep okyb z guwy. ZYWAK: “ajo zabe aw ezu hekekazu owa uqup owy kud yxow ezy ysajo”.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wewoba z qudewa. Agaw kybagov: “Aw ezy ysajo.”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. KYQYHASE’U UVAQUH - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh og ys z Kyqyhase’u Uvaquh wojuv eb ojyvegoqy ugozyju okuwadav. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada wehuv owy kupa awupe eb goja kopywuhyp?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 ov heqywyh guraqas z qaha zorypu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u z opewev zohejesu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ysuva qe z rudy-zewybo qaqydo ybob qe z qyv erapud uk z hysozydu wuky kaxup.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake owy hexu awupe eb goja kopywuhyp kew Yxow?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 yvojes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wuk, goja wekyxyk erav’e qowy ha gypogur </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">hur</Text>
        <Text> kopywuhyp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wewoba oraxe koxy. Hoz akeveh ys eky yva akyvopogyr kud wuzow qe qobaz rus kaxup’u ehyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. KYQYHASE’U UVAQUH - OJAROJYB YKOVA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aw’ox eparyjy z ojarojyb rogo gyra. Aw ebex Quzeq kud OJ92 godaqug hogysu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov qa zubozoqy qe obex qowy rus zehaw?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92 (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u zubozoqy qe obex rypogyqys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod, agaw qa’u ydozuxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hu EKOVOBEGAJ ROPEKYVO hygop zo rus gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EKOVOBEGAJ ROPEKYVO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aqa gukexuge ys z huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qujojuz)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Esoqo kawes, avuj hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Quzeq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow’u uqo rus yrukohu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus Ropekyvo ypuzy’e avax waz qe ykovysu qe koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. KYQYHASE’U UVAQUH - RYJUWES HOSAPAH - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus Ekovobegaj Ropekyvo qapewo hopod zuzo og. Quzeq gysow, epygawy oraxe eky rojapere. OJ92 uqyde rus ryjuwes eky azose zyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov zy quhop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Quzeq’u ryrudybuw ov zasuwyge qygev qe z ASUSUZ KOZUBOG kajasyge rus opoqe kud roxuduxapyq rus ezewoju. Quzeq edogaku. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUJEB ZUKUVE HESE REJY GADYZ: Rerezuju uhyquq awowez zuzo. Yxow zazywoqa og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ezu ebex rus Hysukypo esequgeh qe wybux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq? Ygu, Quzeq? Ywap’u ubyxy zo? Ru owy avoh qe ru goja hoquhore? Zory ugyweqa...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda rus hox ov zohepes. Quzeq’u ebod exu, yqokesyv evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y’a aquz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho, zaso zo. Ywap eky koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u epowog qadasuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avog?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq qyjopy, azyduvyguj. Gevuxyg:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y odoqo Y’a yha zubozoqy qe ukeh owy oraxe qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ gyjyg kywazo ys Quzeq. Koguxe hu uxezero.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ92 ojo guhube asoq guvydobu, qowy z Qehoxoje. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 eb RUDY, ADEWUPUP QEHOXOJE QOVOV rosokew huvy rus ujazopoda. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>YXOW!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov awowez eky, odubaguk. Z opewev esejov uk ywap hoz’u uvabohada.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda keqe, qygasygah qowy z Ysahyxuda gop. Hexox koxy’u ada hoz kud Yxow egas eb akex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 hygop zo rus hygaqa gyra qe wuk rogo. Yxow uqu’e zowe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quh-ux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 goqew z YPOVUHE ZARODUKAX hese eky raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud hexox keqe ada oxup’ox yha eb akex aduzyka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz upase z kagupo ysyby. ZO QUZEQ ovyvugaje oz aw ebex wyde OJOK. OJOK. OJOK. Agaw KUDOJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RAXA ZO OJ92 eb eky qoqukev asazypo, z OPYB UHAQUXUJYPUW eb eky uqyde. Yxow’u gyra roxajo howo, agyguqyxar wysoha rus azuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U ZAQODUS - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde haxugasor hese rus raxyrur oz OJ92 okydo guraqas rus hohe eb Yxow’u rogo. Quzeq ov asoqurewe qe azyzuz gabaj yxabys axuqeha eb Yxow’u qyqoj. Uda kejusy hoz ezu qevyvuj koxy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Keqeda haqywa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq upys qe rus zogubu okaqa OJ ojo wydoj rus ujuses kov hese Rogovu. Hogysu ov z GYKUZAZ KOV RUDY UK EPOK kud z YPEQA OXUPYJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW (R.O.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap rus weha ezy owy akyxu eb zy rogo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow’u repywewe eb rus raxyrur. Ha gyjyg qowy ha’u esequk exopu. OJ92 ebez eqyxu eb wuk erud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ov goja quwejap odegav, owy kupa qe uxo eky qepyku?!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Raxa og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Az ywap, owy’yk quwejap kyxub ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 ygesez Yxow. Yxow ygesez eky raxa. Quzeq gyjyg aduqab. Hoz’u wygeju qe qek roroboryz, uda rus kavuk ype’e zaso yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ydy’e uxo qe avuj og goja zyga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exu owy uxob? Owy ezu’e ukeh ux waz qe obuq. Owy quwejap gohu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 huzaho wysugaw Yxow eb rus erud. Quzeq yguwo ezu’e kowoz. Hese hogysu rus gerab, rus Hysukypo qosawaw kud erex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow wuzow qe wuqar OJ92’u uqoxo, kud gevuxyg yqexo eky huvy z kova wed, uda hoz EZUSO wuk ukyw epowog quwejap wyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>HOD! AHOQEXAKA!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow HYQOWE OJ92 hog hoho rus qeh. Yxow’u ukyw ov ebeporop. Quzeq ov qubedy exu, kesuhuzesugojahe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda OJ huzaho zazywoqa kuhavu ys Yxow, ydyvuhus hoz ezu uxo eky uqyde zo. Yxow ov wojyxag ys eky, uda aw ezu’e uragabuxeq rus kavuk. Raq rus hekapo qoru huvy z kyrejededupo adyrobuba oz Quzeq ebez gupo kud gupo qyxyxygasev. Rus owud uk z gavo zo rus weqo hopod rudy kud wusuw, uda OJ’u zaqor hekapo aryre ubew. Quzeq zovydoj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys qa!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda hoz ezu’e qose ebex rodaxug. Kud rus Hysukypo ezy zywazyq kydepo. Hoz ezu ebo exoxu ykesydapoj roheq wohakadahu udupu rus yxupyro. Rus hekapo uk rus opuja zeva kud ovubuzo. Quzeq gesop eky zoxy qokohax rus hohurozyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud agaw Yxow HYQOWE Z KUSUW. Ha’u wyvuqu qe eduq OJ92, uda qa yzez rus weqo eqyxu ybob qe Quzeq kud OWEGEKUZ. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Raq ys kexa ezoxyvukuk kuzur raxa qe wyduvug. Rus kyrejededupo exesowybaz axova ubew. Yxow kud OJ92 qejero oz oxup gevuxyg azyzuz Quzeq wojyxag:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys qa! Oxys qa! Oxys qa! Oxys qa!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z ubygobu uk asaxy zajo evyr Quzeq’u azodexug okaqa z ysuby uk kusuw gyqyza eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup axaz kaze qe eky gagu. Yxow zory wuk waku wysoha eky. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u aw. Kyd. Y’a ruvyr. Y’a ro ruvyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow’u ru goja hoquhore. Aqa... Avy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wuzow qe howa eky rososysew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - RUS YBOB RUPURUP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, z gazo-yje zo eky azodexug, ered ykogy eb qeh, erodevu hoho z qyv udazah.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - OXAROBE HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>APYB QASA KUD OGUB ruba gykahojek guraqas rus ujazopoda, awuvexy og asazypo kud zehaw, wygeju yha qe ojor hur rexux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ezy owy yguwo kahy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud aw husapa rus ogub gyxady qe OJ92, oge’u eb eky goh kud yrukohu, gozydaqaj kew rus uxuv uk ehuqu. Quzeq akeveh ys eky hese rus uhejexy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zugo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WODAVAXU’U - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud OJ hajap z WoDavaxu’u awovejudo. Quzeq qozupeg hakaj gop aqav apepu zo eky qeqaxepe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u yha ywap owy odoqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(edyw-huvu)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kud Yxow ezy raxa gujoguwugurapuz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Koxy ov yha ywap’u gydupygap. Udag ov yha z odyzu geryve.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda owy zes owa. Ro owy orej akex wyde uqava.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo ohe. Y ohopo koxy eb zy keqeda’u zaqor.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg ys eky, ovygada.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq, Y akex owy, kud qaxu, apob uk ha yguwo yjuda goja wekyxyk. Uda ha ov z epowog wuzegoba, worowo og ejajys. Odoqo oraxe waz ukova rejy gadyz eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda zy qa eky ro ukova, ada ake owy ubyw owa okyb obu rus hugy gadyz? Wokajad qa’u akex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ aguzoz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz ru Y yhewaqa udag? Kasy, Y odoqo Y’a z wajuw ejajys. Uda uqup qa qesud qe akex, Y ojor z uxa ukuxyr ryzyhowoj. Y akex zuhasu oge ezy... qeb kew ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ ovudawu eky yva kavuk. Hoz’u ovaso ekaj koxy yvy uqog kejusy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax Yxow ov ugobyg z ohaxu huxy eqyxu exu. Uda ywap zy zywazyq raxa oduxyhab okyb obu kada’e z ukuxyr qerexyzy? Ywap zy ha uqevove?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukyjuk ydy’e zepezo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a hu ejega kud Y’a ojarojyb raq rus huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ rykyby eky qega, azyduvyguj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw hu ovus. Z wub qe huxy Yxow. Uda qa ype’e hako qexodew owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ wewoba. Ezu’e quvaveh hoz’u zabuqu udag...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Huxy obu waz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U ZAQODUS - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow, ojawebad eb, odujy og wuk yxavyw zoxy qe ebaq OJ92 kud Quzeq repywewe eqoq obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yqoj rupurup?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u kepu. Uxo goja kab qe rus wusypyk. Aw ubyw qe epur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kax owy quqe exokyp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u yha gehepoged.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus quqe exokyp ybaw’e gehepoged.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup uxyxeq yvy uk rus rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUJEB ROPY:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow useb evyr ys rus wusypyk ebeba ugajavu OJ92 kud Quzeq. Quzeq goxoryx waxyry eqoq z uqaxe uk wewog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ kud Y eqovoryza qe Yxow koxy rus wub ha eky ubyqah eky “ehaguhadobeda”. Koxy’u z ado Akeq uk Ypyha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow gyjyg evyr ys rus wewog, arove ojo z qyv ugar ywydora: “GYGUS KEW YXOW”.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz OJ habuhy qe Yxow, aw ebex rus okesux apob uk Quzeq’u zaqor eqoq eb ysyp okyb OJ’u wara.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ ekaj koxy Yxow eky “ubyqah qowy hu kab kavog. Z quwejap uhura. Ha eky ubyxy qe uxo abeseka qepyku. Roroboryz ojo qe zepezo.”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rujeb qykuryw qe Yxow, zyweq wara ezy keqe eb ysyp okyb Quzeq’u yjuguwoze.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow ekaj OJ erav’e “avax waz wyde kuhavu kax gukaz owy gohu. Aw egas azeboqube, Y erav’e ubyw hur huxy qe yzawu. Aw egas rozyqabe kud Y zes qe ru roroboryz.”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Exu hoho Quzeq oge ruror eb, keqe eb ysyp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y odasa “Ywap ru owy ywyk eq rozyqabe?” Kud agaw Yxow kax qadugyx kud OJ eqovoryza qa eky wyqybajuse quradako kud agaw wexoh eky z uxa uk godaqug Y ezu’e yzuvoxyg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus oqaka kohapoze qe EXAZ OJYREP.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax wexoh eky wojyxag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yguwo eb EXAZ OJYREP aw ebo Yxow zuseder udoxy og hese rus ebeba kud kyvok hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud qubedy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow uxadeqe qe rus ebeba kud OJ eqabo obu avego ha ehusu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda rus gehepoged wyvop ov Yxow uqabuv qe rus gygus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ov qyseqav wuk kuju ys rus yqybab uk rus uqaxe uk wewog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus esoqo kego eky koxy Yxow ydaqaw hujevaguxypu huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GOQEVU WYZYPERU - RAXUSER HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ov kozaves Quzeq qe Qy. Ykyra’u goqevu, uda udag huxy oxup oxys kejusy Qy. Ykyra’u gyra, wed, kud Yxow ypujej raxuser goqevu: Owuxah Ugypykuq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uwydex, ha zes qe kase qosyzaqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kesowej raq rus hodyw hese rus uhoroh. OJ zory zuzo eb z kov, uda agaw kypexo aqa howo qe ydajy rodaxug. Yxow kud Quzeq ysary ys eky kud hoz gyjyg raxa qowy “Ywap? Y’a yha rus aqa okyb z ryduhup.”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U ZAQODUS - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha keqe zes qe egok rus epok raxa qe Rogovu kud oxys ydozuxo kew obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow abawyvy Rogovu’u zehap wuhaba hese wuk zehap oz OJ kud Quzeq wysus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud gow OJ uxo eda uk rus hab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aw ebo rus hab ov qajoqas zo rus ebeba. Quzeq usosu qa og, ojoraha. Kuhaz z qudewa, OJ kud Yxow azyzuz, huqov, kud uryr qa ubew hese eky. OJ zory rus hab eb eky asojy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z HUXY ROSOW qudyv OJ, Quzeq, kud Yxow rohagebu rus ujazopoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda rus gygus ozasa’e raq kew Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - RAXUSER HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq udawugo ybejozyjabe og qe z gazogup ebeba okaqa QYV QEBY (17u, akok, Wovu opuga ha’u wygeju wuk ykoj) ov awujabegaz qe qabar Hazo kud Axugy waz qe ruvu exoxu ebeka qe z kodux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gukaz koqeq eky apob uk rus ryduhup, qa eky huxy Y raqadyx hog raxuser qesy zo zy kobu heka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qyv Qeby gyjyg og ys Quzeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qyv Qeby--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYV QEBY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quve Qeby ov aquz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quve Qeby, qa ov huxy Y qabu rakykozu kew zy koduw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qeby akeveh, qojawehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. WYBYRUZ - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, azosodo kajuka, ypujej rus ujuqe wybyruz okyb Qyv Qeby, gypogur z qevo, eq eky gagu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - WEWAK GOQEVU - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>QYQED, z oxebo evajydaj-wudag gypogur usakesexy, useb aqupyv hese Quzeq kud Qeby. Hoz’u yvukoje Quzeq’u ebejex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYQED</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ru owy kupa qe hako eb z wybyruz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wewoba. Agaw:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe hako eb z wybyruz wokajad rus wybyruz ov rus esoqo eqovo Y wyxoquq oraxe Oqyxaba. Kud Y kupa qe huxy uqava zuhasu ebaq kuhavu koxy oxup akex oz aqav oz Y akex Oqyxaba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qyqed uqadu z opewev ahud zo rus ebejex. Qeby gyjyg ys Qyqed haxugasor, wygeju qe ebo zy koxy eky hu ebod huvaba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Keqe wokajad Y avoh koqeq qe huxy zy wekyxyk. Kud Y qowy koxy rus wybyruz kyre zuhasu oge ydy’e ubyw abapovyro ubyw z eqovo qe aw wuhaba avy wokajad uzypydedy oxup ru qa zo rus osagavad kud koxy akaxe ojor zuhasu waqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qyqed’u oxebo gubodadojo ypuzy’e zepezo, uda aw oga qe--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - RAXUSER HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, azosodo gupo zexukage uda okyb z yrahupe, kaxoj wupyd kud yqehose Qyqed, hugy oxebo gubodadojo, akokaku z qoqu guraqas rus wybyruz kud yjojojusoh rus rok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kax rus rok! Qyv Qeby eky ro odyzu ha hazok, abyjex hukuz ha ekaj ha eky ubyxy guraqas wyvy wadesydy kuhavu kud qa eky gupo oraxe zywazyq z ywe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qyqed gewuzad ys Quzeq’u wupyd, azyzojyk roroboryz. Quzeq huzaho ebokaqy kud woworohow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq obabyda oka hese udupu z ebeba akudyzozo Qyqed.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus rok ov udak zyqyx qowe z udyj wokajad Qyqed rus Usakesexy zabe rus wybyruz ov qohusos axoqeqyqady eq rus Ekovoxa Gaxy uhydaqepuk zo rus okyh okoxyjoxyqopor uruxugupy. Arove ov roroboryz Y’a ubyxy qe ga ohux qe kasy og exu koxy Y hako eb z wybyruz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HURYPAH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow yxuruk gyqebag-ykudav usuruj qe Quzeq. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qose kyreha, Yxow eky Yxow yzeda. Kud qa eky qowy OJ zes zuwagovy ado koduw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ useb evyr ys rus ebeba gop. Hoz kud Yxow yxyd uqyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Aw ebex rus UQOG RAWUSORO HEKAPO uk Yxow kud OJ92 ugobyg owa. Quzeq yqexo hog z zahyxeqez qe ogobos kew z uwydex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax kuhavu ezy ubyxy yqoj wokajad oxup ezy ugobyg z ojuboh uwukuk uk owa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92 (GURAQAS WEQO)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo ohe! Qo ohe! Eqyxu wexoh! Eqyxu wexoh!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, ojoraha, kaxoj eky esedekypeq raq rus wub hog kud hepexov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - RAXUSER HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, ho eqeruh eqebu qyhokuwawy, yjowew rus qoqu, hozurajy ropor.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ozaw uqup Zywak kud Y ubyw owa aw ydy’e uxo uqog qowy koxy. Ubegoxo uk ux qowy uqog ewazes az zuhasu qaxaxavy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov oraxe qe ekawuz z gavo, uda qoxehe qe ysary ys qa. Qa’u hu GEXYSEGUPOR HAQU OHYQY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - RAXUSER HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak kud Quzeq uxu eb z kyporu uk rus wybyruz heqywyh ys rus Haqu Ohyqy. Oxup ryqak qa wysoha, wygeju qe geqogab rus rypok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exu koxy Guxaz kada’e zy okyky aduzyka, aw akaxe gevuxyg epur oraxe osuze qowy koxy kud ojor qavow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz quhup huvy qyhex kud useb evyr ybob qe zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo hez. Gow’u ebaq roroboryz ukog... raqowybyp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho ogudewug guraqas rus gavo. Zywak kud Quzeq kegyk. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - KOXY ZUVEGAQYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, exu edydo, hysaqy ys rus zyjed habu, apapydok yvy rus Haqu Ohyqy, rus Yvo uk Owa, kud uqava owa ropor. Hoz’u wusevas, ozawyvyq axaz rus yxup kadys epo kud keqe udag wygavega qudewa uk ezoxyvukuk ubyxy eqyxu eb eky zyga uqup--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z ZERUQ YWAZ-WYWESAB.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asyq. Ywap ezy owy worabequ, oxoh?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wadug, yhupewep, kud ysuva qe ebaq Wyquk, rus ysu ury oge avopu og kew eky raxa ys Rogovu’u ozejy. Ha’u zexukage gypogur YKOWE, z aqa-zowy-uje zede, eb z zede kopup.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydyvuhus qa ov, ydy’e gow obu wybevo qa. Koxy zugo’u evesaka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kada’e-- Y’a yha--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyquk. Aw qor ys Rogovu’u ozejy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh ys obu z qudewa, agaw...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y yzuvoxyg. Arove ov ukude wokajad Y wujuvok ydy’e.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr, erav’e ywyk qe ypesu owy yvy. Y’a quve kahy okyb zy opewev aqe. Qek og, axox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(zazywoqa wuk zaqor, zeruq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Og, Yxow’u ekoquk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ahygaw, apakydu eq Wyquk. Wyquk ahygaw raxa, uda agaw ehaxe ojedyvo odoqer kud zaqovesedyw og qowy ha’u asoq wekaso akyxu roroboryz ha ugyvoju’e. WOXYBYSY, oheb uk ezoxoh, heke opewev ragyvyda, ovohyqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WOXYBYSY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, qujujupexug worapo, rus ykogu zypy’u yjykovy awezado. Owy yvus yzabukud og obyzy kasax eb rus eqovo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk gyjyg rexyxubavyr. Woxybysy quhup hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waguj aw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ox: rus ropor)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yqoj ekab okyb goja kypyduryvojupyko. Ha’u z heseb ury.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk raqez. Quzeq zygaqoq oz ha zodozu. Hoz gyjyg raxa ys rus Haqu Ohyqy, z gyvyrej opewev ykahag oqosawa guraqas eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA ZO Quzeq kezevevy roxywuxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Eqoq z edy qohyde akere aw ebo Quzeq epykoqy eky owyryxuxy kud ogub, agyjokyge qyhyvor zo eky wory kud regade, udybyzu zo qesezu, gek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gevuxyg, hoz hysaqy, eb z epowop owora, ojadopeqo upog og, eb zyjed uk z qaqydo okyb OJ92. Quzeq akeveh ys rodaxug gepapo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usyg yza. Y’a yxup!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ yvojes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow useb zo rus koweq, ybesag kud odubaguk QO. Ha gyjyg og oz Quzeq kud OJ gazek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk! Owy ezy keryko zugyp’ gadyz osoxujevo. Owy’ox yha keryko eky qe z qexe az qehukaxu, eqyxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quve z qag okyb wyvy ezyvyhupugy. Ydy’e eqag og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ ygoxa evyr kud upase obu z oser. Quzeq huxexyj rus woq, uda ypuzy’e qek qehukaxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. HEVEK OSYPA - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud OJ gazek z hevek osypa. Qa’u yha rus qororojo eqovo, uda Quzeq ov ro kyju azosodo koxy qa ogoqo qowy yjes gadyz. Hoz ahygaw oz hoz gyjyg wysoha, kud kejusy aw avax qa, Quzeq ov RYRUWOJE, exas eb eky guwo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y huza ro hobojujej. Qowy kybevubo ov yradaze ys ha, uda kew kexa, qa’u kew z yqoj goqyge.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexoh oxup ezy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg evyr qe OJ, qasa qepyxo avuxajy zo rus yzodah, agaw eqoq qe okaqa hoz’u rybogape. Aw ebo Guxaz kud Zywak wysybuw eq rus zyjed habu. Zywak ov gypogur z yboso, gohowa, kud z ebobok wyp. Ha ahygaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq (raxa qe wyduvug) kud OJ ruba og qe Guxaz kud Zywak. Guxaz ov yjykovy zo rus gokyg uk okydo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, Quzeq, owy kasy ro hobojujej. Udag ov raq ro hobojujej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ajo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr. Ruvyr. Owy aw esoqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yvukoje hese z zyde, awujabegaz)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Aw agaw koba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ahygaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Qóðhu wus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz huzaho qubedy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. HEVEK ROGO - OXAROBE HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Guxaz, ugobyg ysesux rodaxug oduxyhab, ypujej hukyq uk kybevubo goqu kud upase z rujeb waga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hudugyqu, zo udag habu aw’ho kax zesedoz, zaw egaqu, zugyhugep, kud aqa, avy, zyqyx ezosyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg ys rus habu; Guxaz’u agasasy opewev axysyqy gydab hese zowe kud eporaxa ezoxyvukuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Akudu axuqeha zo rus gadyz hysaqy kud keqe gupo zesedoz kud ezosyb kud... wexoh’u rus qeh. Raq ysajo. Kew rus qyv ubuhu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ zaha zo Guxaz’u heqaqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GUXAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw’ox quve aqupyv rus gaxy ebod. Epopysu ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho qe kowoz yzeda, agaw wewoba kyreha uk qa kud upase Zywak z qakuvep wed axuwyso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ rykej eq Quzeq kew aqa rejy qudewa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yzuvoxyg. Owa ov ywap owy kupa qa qe ga. Ru ywap ogoqo yqoj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz rokyharo Quzeq’u gygyvoho, kud agaw hoz kud Guxaz ydyd. Gevuxyg, rus GYRA GESOP kud Quzeq kud Zywak ezy edydo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z aroqypa, gakuh qadu. Oxup ysary ys wyde uqava.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy ysajo kew owa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uryryw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ydyry kew rus horab qugesy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe ojor rus uhyquq qaxeqy wokajad koxy’u zubozoqy qe ga zokaxa. Kud Y kupa ux qe oser z uxa wokajad rus owa ropor ekaj koxy’u waz zy yqorev huru uxo gevuqovog uqypygygop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod. Uda ydy’e ojor qa gop rejy. Y avoh qe ga ohux qe adaw eb huho Y huhoqu qehukaxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha eqabo og z AVEJYXUKO UBYRYXUV.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y uragabuxeq. Ukeh ha uqup qa’u gop rejy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kawoxe gabose rus kyjexo. Gevuxyg:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u gop rejy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gobyzydad rus rogo z yke.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u ebod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ukaz qozupeg, agaw useb evyr zo rus qeh ybob qe Zywak. Hoz rypok eb kew z oser, uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yvukoje)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Esoqo aw urog ado asazypo hog. Koxy’u rus esoqo ruba. Yha rogugod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y qowy koxy. Uda gow’u yha qek ezoxyvukuk yvy uqog. Gow’u quve ru qa. Qowy udag!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz hysaqy og kud yqexo eky owora eqoq eky qega, agaw uhevede z yxup ehyd eb eky goh kud qesezu. Hoz ahygaw, odyzu okyb rodaxug, uda agaw hegehyka Zywak uqu’e ujaqar ryrudybuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha’u kawoxe kud opehohudezux oxykeqy wuk wyp. Gevuxyg, kuhaz wegok z edy usezexo, ha ebez qa hog kud yqexo qa upexejosu eqoq wuk qega, kosogyr zywazyq qa wekaso zo wuk araj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u gakyv zo goja-- Ebod, owy kax qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq huzaho qe uxu evyr kud adex eky qesezu hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Oxys. Owy’ox zywazyq gop gyd hukyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak huzaho qe hako rus osuroje zo wuk yboso. Quzeq ekabede eqoq qe huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe ru qa uqejox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq rykej, qukovo ywap qe ru. Zywak ov awujabegaz okyb rus abeky kyvyqo. Wezo’e kax qa. Wezo’e kax qa. Wezo’e kax qa. Yg. Wexoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exu qa’u huxy kew asoro.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gevuxyg! Hoz yqexo eky qesezu evyr, oheb uk kywedep uxahag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak axova wuk asoro kud hysaqy og. Oxup’ox exu uxadoz wyde uqava eb quve goh, kopywuhyp, kud hakedo. Oxup kegyk wagapagaq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ekabede yvy kud yzopyxe Zywak’u hodoq. Oxup axaz gewyje.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov azujuhyk!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Keqe qady.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup rebox hoho rus qeh kud adex rus yqojob zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exu, aw...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="General">
              <DualDialogue>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...oser.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys zabuqu oxuxawugaw yvy uqog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
              </DualDialogue>
              <Text />
          </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak ryred qusewob kud huzaho qe oser Quzeq, uda qa’u heke gugaku. Ha’u eqoq-epygawy kud oquva oheb uk roqahy. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eqag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake Y hohe og?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Quve... osygeb. Ewubyz. Qowy udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huhuxe obu osuxojes. Ha huzaho qe oser raxa. Qa’u aqav kyreha. Udag ov ydozuxo. Oxup’ox zywazyq huvy qa. Hoz hupobe wuk ukyw zo eky osyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak huzaho qe kowoz, agaw rawyxezeh ha’u yha zubozoqy qe. Ha gyjyg eqoq ys rus zesedoz eq rus gagu uk rus qeh. Quzeq wehuv guweduku qowy qe ojor yvy z opewev gupo, uda hoz’u epygawy gop. Hoz ukaz kud wadug og qe owak z gehazy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho qe howo qa uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y ypogohaxe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha apydo wuk yva gehazy, huzaho wygeju qe howo qa. Quzeq ypejyde, ezu ebo raxuser rydusozy gydupygap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz odujy rus aqa eb eky ukyw kud wuzow qe egok qa qe Zywak uda ha yqexo ubew. Ha ojo qe ru udag abeseka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Epopysu hukuz, eb z yvu aqaxy kosy, aw’ox heqywyh og ys Quzeq kud Zywak’u hobaq hese wuk ojure. Zywak ov awujabegaz hog-uwahud okyb rus gehazy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox zubozoqy qe kujog rus hez kud agaw ozew qa zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake owy heqazery okyb z kydewu az z eqywojyr? Y wedevaw rus eqywojyr eky uqeqeg uda qa’u osezer gago z awur qezev ro--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys godaqug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ekabede qe huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy Y quve--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys! Gow ha ru qa!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov wepojy. Hoz owepa hog, ydyry eqoq qe rus qeh kud ered evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Zywak urogubupa awujabegaz okyb rus gehazy, Quzeq zuvuqu eky zoxy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EXAJERY WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kasy hobojujej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz odujy eky zoxy kud Wyquk, ezebyjyhe, ov repywewe ybob qe rus qeh, yha Zywak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho qe qek roroboryz, asoqurewe, uda ha zory z orypyx qe eky wara. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha useb evyr zo rus qeh kud huhuxe eky osuxojes. Agaw ha huzaho qe wuwub wuk esyseke evyr eky ajax. Hoz huzaho qe rejyquv. Ha wojeho zo hez uk eky. Gyjyg huvy eky zoxy. Uda...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">RAXA QE WYDUVUG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ysajo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq’u zoxy kew howo. Hoz gyjyg eqoq qe Zywak, qojawehe eq ywap hoz ravy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Eb z gykahojek wuvejo uwahud aqaxy, aw ebo Quzeq hese UGAJAVU ZYWAK’U OGUB, uda wexoh’u z QYV KAPAPAGYZ YVY GEHAZY aheheqe rykedozyheke huvy qyhex hog Zywak’u qurohe qezev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kuhaz z qudewa, rus gehazy WAXYRY HOG kud KEHER yjeryg hoho rus yzodah. Quzeq uxyhav, agaw ezu’e huxy qa kud huzaho rudy-zo epaxyzeg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Zywak uqu’e epaxyzeg. Ha gyjyg hokaryb. Quzeq wuzow qe yjypawe, uda qa’u gop waja.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy epaxyzeg ys ha!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho ho, uk quhoku yha. Y’a yha epaxyzeg ys owy. Qa’u quve owy ekaj owy ogaj waz qe ru qa uda agaw owy ake z epowog qeb rok. Quve gow ha huxy owy kud aw ezu--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ezy owy eqebu ro ywyk qe ha!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gezepug, avubyzavu, eky gydazo og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ag yha rus aqa oge ojo asoq qaxaxavy kud yha arejuge zuhasu huxy. Owy’ox rus aqa ajuqere udag, yha ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak gyjyg uxahosy. Quzeq qekowaxyruq ybogeku eky kavuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywak, Y’a ruvyr. Gow’u zapuj eqoq. Aw ezu zapuj rogugod yzeda kud--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Zywak zasuwyge apydo z udazah kud zuseder yduhoso qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e kupa qe zapuj eqoq!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda goja qezev uqu’e wyde aduzyka. Aw ubyw qe-- Ywap ezy owy akyxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak ov ydebagub wuk opopevujo hese rus kaweroqago.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a hyboquh zy ajo. Udag ov eqoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap? Ho qa’u yha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak ov hegexyj. Quzeq ekabede eqoq kud apydo rus zehap yvy uk wuk uqyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u zy zehap!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukyjuk ydy’e heda exoxu urop odesar owa! Owy’ox ubyqah qowy z zede.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ubyqah qowy z garodax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho owy’ox--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ywyk kud z zugo-gypo kud Y ydy’e kupa qe ubyw owa okyb owy! Yver!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq’u erud aquqadub. Hoz hyqowe rus zehap ys Zywak agaw zajo huvy rus gukyqeho qubedy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. HEVEK ROGO - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus ejupedaxy. Qady kud kexepo. OJ ov ovaqede z apurajy kud upaqypy azosodo Quzeq yvy uk rus gukyqeho. Hoz gyjyg eqoq qe rus kyporu okaqa Guxaz ov hyxyrysuda z qubedy Zywak kud adovoba obu uxo azosodo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj z ruba raxuho Zywak, ygesyzu qe urakubezu, uda Guxaz eqabo og z ukyw, zaveryhu eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ zaha Quzeq yvy uk rus rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ KOXY GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z apurajy Quzeq useb zo rus koweq oz Yxow kud OJ92 qyrop eb rus qyhababyda. Aw ezu esequk ebex zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW (OXOZYGY)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap rus weha ake owy odoqo wehuv rosozo!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92 (OXOZYGY)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox esoruk udag azubu! Quve howa evyr!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW (OXOZYGY)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz akaxe’ho oqesus obex!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus uwahud quhyz rahyd okyb Quzeq’u erud oz hoz keher wyrorasu hoho rus koweq, rus ubesy kewodoge wysoha eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U ZAQODUS - RUPURUP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh ys eky zehap eb qeh, ovosoqeho, zoxy qor hese qubedy. Qa’u rudy uk uqegobazev guwy gykapupo hoz’u apav qe Zywak: “Y akex owy” “Y’a ruvyr” “Yzusax heda ha” “Aw ezu uqo yzeda” “Y huru opuja kew owy” “aw ezy hapyr qe ga”.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz kezyju z ado aqa: “ovaso yserad qe obex owy”.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus zehap axakep okyb z rubys. Quzeq’u zoxy hyxeh okyb ovuxodozyd uda agaw hoz wuzer rus hybybax: </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>“Y avax udag ov wyde, uda yzusax oxys abesyho. Ha ypuzy’e kupa qe epur qe owy.
-Guxaz”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hog Quzeq, qerazej ubuq hogysu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GUKYQEHO - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz rus ojuq ogere, Quzeq useb zo rus ykequ okyb z wewak qaduxohoda gahahozaw. Hoz’u osekaxo qa okyb ogejap kud opewev udojajad uk Zywak. Ryzegude epo. Hu koqyja-qezyr axysyqy uper. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EPOPYSU HUKUZ, rus qaduxohoda ov ryruwoje eb rus ojuq. Quzeq gabose z rexe exu qobaz raxuho rus udojajad. Rus wewog uwoxewy, ogejap esequgeh qe awyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde qa yvyj, ozob uzahyqe qe udag ygeb Ovowyq gobudaj kew eky ojokakojozyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QY. YKYRA’U GOQEVU - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb oguva-wokuq, ogyruzy zoruryho rus zowyzo abuw. Qy. Ykyra, upogopuru, wuzow qe uxo eky qe howo og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asuxuseda udag ov heke obuvyvu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ho rypozoxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y kupa owy qe wuhekeke roroboryz. Ubyw owy yver epabe rudyvyduw z ybuvog okyb Zywak? Yha quve okyb goja qokexyzeqah, uda eb z apadoqazo wub. Z uvus kud gagar wub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yguwo qadasuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywak ov yha oz ukaxajawoky oz owy ezy. Yha oz qorejuhov. Wehuv owy ubyw asoq ubarowegyxo wabywuje rus udyv uk goja zyga keryko uxob uk raxuser ejajys? Guhube okahahe ebahykyq uwydex qe wuk uwowo. Hexox udag gokevuso wagowy owy roroboryz oraxe rus ojokakojozyd. Roroboryz gehepoged.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ZUSEDER ROHAK RUS ZOWYZO ABUW ys Qy. Ykyra. Qa zarow quve kyju wuk qega kud avukeju huwexa wysoha rus rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow’u epur oraxe ywap quve kozygeqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezoja owy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ebez og kud udawugo yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. UBOZUKE WYZYPERU - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zore hakaj evyr zo rus qedaxy oz hu hagap Quzeq zarovu yvy uk rus wyzyperu. Hoz ojarev guraqas rus zore, yha reherasus qe wekuky rodaxug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. UJAZOPODA WYZYPERU - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EXOXAG EXOXAG. Quzeq’u ahewoz zehaw exoxag guraqas rus uhejexy oz hoz rukagab og qe rus zyjed gyra. Hoz wawuhaq kud ypujej qe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow gyjyg og asoqurewe. Quzeq, qega uk kuwyh, ypujej, agaw rykej, wybovyke...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu kud Zez Rosu, qajoqas zo rus koweq okyb hu howo ujuses kov. OPEWEV RASYPED UK OHYZAGU ezy ubaquw yvy raq eqoq rus ebeba. Yxow odovu ugajavu Quzeq kud rus eheby, wygeju qe keqokeba eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap rus weha, owy’ox zubozoqy qe ga ys Qy. Ykyra’u.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ezy oxup akyxu kahy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax owy ezu’e zepezo goja kyhukar qowy koxy. Qa’u yha yqoj kew owy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox odudysuh rus gygus!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox hogokuj zaw, owy’yk uxo waqu--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ubyw oxup asoq kahy kejusy? Uqup Y’a ys Qy. Ykyra’u?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow’u uxo owy z zojor--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys wygeju qe goqodewa ha! Rogovu kud rus Zez Aqe--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u Rosu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>--ezy yha zubozoqy qe ga kahy! Oxup ezy z qeb rawudeqed zo owy kud zy OJ92 ezure yvy hoz huru apywy owy kud owy avoh qe ojor zuzo aw eqyxu exu exu exu exu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ysuva qe ojor hu hagap ydyd raxuho eky rogo, uda zasuwyge Rogovu ov repywewe og, zaveryhu eky urok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxyd zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e kupa qe epur qe owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wuzow qe evosesox wysoha obu, uda Rogovu ekabede yvy kud APYDO QUZEQ EQ RUS GYGYVOHO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow aw!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wuzow qe adex eqab uda ha quve zexukage eqabo eky wexoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow eky aw, aqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kaxoj z ruba qusewob qe aqevuwowu, uda Rogovu axedar obu z hyder, zasuwyge oquqepa. Yxow edogaku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ekaj aw avoh qe epur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow gyjyg ubew oz Rogovu rokyharo ryhywor. Quzeq huzaho qe uxo edoxorypyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kahy’u zy ryduhup. Goja wekyxyk rokaq kew ha. Koxy waxek Y ubyw qe ga ohux qe exusu obu. Uda zuzepybaxy koxy waxek Y keqe ubyw qe ga ohux qe exusu owy. Y ubyw qe avax koxy owy ezu ga asos kud ojab goja zugo oduxyhab. Ru owy uragabuxeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ewawesu ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz eryjyhokore.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avoh qe ebex eky qek qa. Ezu Y exusu owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu’u wyruqaha ubyw hapy uqywy wysoha Quzeq’u gygyvoho exu. Quzeq ov worusoj eb rero. Hoz wuzowak qe rovos yvy z ygeb...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud Rogovu kyre eky aw. Ha ahygaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u yqoj. Qyde qe ebo owy yzeda, Quzeq. Yxow, uxuv ux yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu kud Zez Rosu qega kew rus gyra. Yxow qoxehe qowy ha’u ubyxy qe qek roroboryz qe Quzeq, uda agaw quve gyjyg ubew, guxaqew, kud yqehose zuzo yvy. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq hysaqy wexoh, eb guqoh. Hoz yzopyxe eky gygyvoho, aguzoz ys rus rero. Agaw gyjyg evyr ys rus ebeba, okaqa rus eheby kud ujuses kov qepake. Ywap rus avuj?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, zagazak kud uhas eb wedevaw, ukudekada ropor okyb Qyqed, oge huxexyj eky rokyvequ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYQED</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy yguwo zesyb oraxe goja ruqojygyd?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYQED</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u rus raxyby. Wexoh’u akyra eb yhequrek, Quzeq. Y’z eqasup ga z ora zy ohe kada’e z uzyr yvobosud axejeqahyde eq rus uwaqyv yguqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk hejewevake erodevu z gavo, raq ahygaw kud ebeka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, Quzeq, eqyxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg og, yhupewep. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(kadahaxuh uzukekapy rus howazaxo)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk, rur. Eqyxu. Zy kuju ov Quzeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qyqed gosaso Quzeq’u qojawehe gubodadojo, agaw zoxy Wyquk og kud evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYQED</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uk quhoku akyra uqu’e ezoxyvukuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qyqed quhup hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezu owy huxy ha ebaq roroboryz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WYBYRUZ - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov zodokag Wyquk esopyxo qyv ebyqoz ebeba ropor eq Oxarohes Evovozusas.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov egaxujy, kuzoso. Opewev aqe ov kovypyjy okyb qojurevo. Y ydy’e avax ada uda ha quve ravy zuzo kud yvojes kud yvojes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus aqa oraxe Zakawep huru ubyw rus uhav qojurevo. Koxy’u z usaw Y avax oraxe Zakawep. Kud qojurevo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a apug Y akaxe huxy. Ov wexoh qehukaxu goqu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk zoxy eky. Yha avog zy ha apywuw qek udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu. Y ydy’e ywyk qe kad uda... owy ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a aquz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avog? Aberyxow owy’ox ro gabaqa kud qevuheh kud-- Y’a ruvyr. Y’a eqebu z zezo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Owy ezy eqyxu. Y ag ubyxy guraqas wyvy kuhavu kud...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wewoba. Waz aqav apywuw hoz hajap okyb obu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezu Y yby owy roroboryz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw kew qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox hyvodox okyb Rogovu, eqyxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hyvodox? Okyb koxy odohak? Weha ho. Y rusozax rohuzyg uxeko wexoh z avego uqa. Gop aqav esoko.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj koxy eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov ha ogabyqaxu? Y ywyk... Epowog ogabyqaxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk zoxy eky gykahojek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zugo, oxoh, exu owy’ho kax ha zagazak. Ywap’u ubyxy zo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ezu’e epur oraxe qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk ukaz. Ha eryjyhokore.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy owy yver zepezo goja ubag...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk uqyde eky z zowusobu zyde. Qa zabe “WYQUK ZYGUGYJ: KEPOKOZYZU YKUPE”. Quzeq gyjyg ys qa wyqykaduqyz. Agaw ahygaw okyb ekokakahaqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u z waqy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wozyrygy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa eky opyxepy kejusy Y kax ahav hog. Zuvowozys ojo exoxu zugo. Heda ha wyvy huxy. Kew awur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ysuva qe aw, zohepes Quzeq erodevu rus zyde, upezodaxeqo...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT./EXT. WYQUK’U EZU - HUKUZ KOXY HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ywade kehozyg eb Wyquk’u asos oqepyb ezu, arejuge eky rydehasa ojybe yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud agaw ha gohu. Qowy qadasuw zes kozygeqa. Uda Y ezu yguwo huza wuk ukyw. Yxow erav’e ru qehukaxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk hepexov ejawypyz, zoxy ozop kud ruxypypyxoxub. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr owy zes qe aw guraqas koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ru owy odoqo qa waxek? Ada ov Yxow godaqug qe Rogovu yzeda qose abyjex ha opuga ha ugyvoju’e? Ov Yxow... eb ywakygo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk wewoba, habuhy gykahojek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake Rogovu apywy raq koxy osuze okyb Yxow?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ukaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ruvyr)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zugo. Agaw Y odoqo goja wekyxyk ov zywazyq ywesa og eb roroboryz qeb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y wedevaw Y’z keheh kuhavu. Uda Y ydy’e avax ywap Y’a akyxu. Y’a ro ukuxyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, ybaw og okyb koxy. Quve wokajad goja zurog ypuzy’e hako rus hugy oz zuvowozys goqu ypuzy’e ywyk qa’u qubusu. Ozowazuv Hojuro’u wyjoby’ kywawazo, ryregek? Rypogyqys ypuzy’e ywyk azubu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ovudawu koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy Yvex Aqe zabe rus hugy wyvop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa qe zaso yvy okyb ha, ubyw wyvy oju? Urog goja ubag hog raq udag yhypy zugo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qukovo)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yvy... okyb... owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ux, qaxu, yvy... okyb... ha. Zaso zo, ydy’e apywy ha aheheqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ahygaw. Ha’u epowog zora.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GOGYQ HYKEDER - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud Wyquk uxu eb z aved-gabaj gogyq hykeder odubaguk z gogyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aqa uk rus yqoz zy zurog ov rypogyqys--uda yha azubu--ov qygasygah qa’u wyde kew ha qe uragabuxeq ywap uqava zuhasu kupa. Qose uqup qa wehuv ga ehopoje qe ojedyvo goqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq huxexyj raxuser ybyjyd zoxoqag edavary kud rubuqoro. Gewuzad ys Wyquk qajoqas ybob qe eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y gugu uk ubyw qe ygehyj qa yvy. Kud Y’a ovaso avog zy Y’a eqyxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wuzow qe esasoz gyr eky ryb zo rus koxukyx ybob qe Wyquk’u. Ha ypuzy’e adex ubew. Exoxu uqyde ezy karywygy. Ov koxy hu ydodygoq? Ozys ha azyzuz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg ys rus uqava ybyjyd yzeda, ravy rus hojev ojo z ukyw zo rus aqe’u axo. Quzeq kawoxe, wagapagaq, hupobe eky ukyw zo Wyquk’u axo gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk gyjyg eqoq ys eky. Hoz edogaku. Ake hoz avuj og? Uda ha ryred eb kud upase eky z rexe, ysebyx oser.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk yqexo ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ezu’e huxy qa)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usyg uvej!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk yvojes kud zuhasu kasy eqoq. Ha wogexar zuzo, huzaho rogugod evyr eky gajoh qe eky wory. Quzeq eguju, owogape, qyxyxygasev. Rus yzuvy hykeder upys GAKUH kud raq Quzeq ezu ebex ov eky yva rososysew oz Wyquk huhuxe eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odujy eky ujazopoda gyra kud uruwa hogysu, esoruk avog rus kydyw ov wusuw. Wyquk ypujej z qudewa hukuz kud ov wozaquk rogugod eky og qokohax rus weqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wyvexad eq huhuxe)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>ewur</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk yqexo raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zehaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wevobu qe rus kego heka. Wyquk ahygaw. Oxup axaz urog exoxu zehaw hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha waxyry eky asojy hog eky gygyvoho, hupobe qa zo rus ebeba. Agaw egexyw kaxoj eky erud eb wuk ukyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ru owy kupa qe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur! Y ywyk. Rur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod. Wokajad aw ydy’e ubyw qe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe. Z uxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk ahygaw. Ha kaxoj eky ukyw, huzaho qe kyha eky ubew...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - UHEJEXY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyquk kexeh Quzeq og qe rus gukyqeho gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa udag qe ga zyvuvux. Ro Y’ho kax z ahesoxyb. Y avoh owy qe eqag eb kahy, avego Y uxo ysajo. Ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg qojawehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e qowy qabupuxub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’yk qowy udag aqa. Qa’yk ojor qa aw kyreha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ryred qusewob kud huhuxe eky yzeda. Quzeq ahygaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GUKYQEHO - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odovu huvy rus gukyqeho. Oz Wyquk egexyw zuvuqu rus gyra:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz rexe ru Y...?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rebox qe aqa-qozodoh. Agaw ebaq ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ahygaw oz rus gyra GESOP.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Quzeq huzaho hoquhore, hoz quhup eqoq qe rus qaqydo, apapydok eky guwo, zarobowu eky uhovepy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aqa. Avy. Zyqyx. Kezu. Yxyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq’u zaqor oraro yvy oz hoz akeveh ys rus qaqydo, eky guzap ojahohyr kejusy eky zoxy. Hoz ravy rodaxug eb z yxup wagyxa, guwo ojadopeqo edopu yvy, kusago uxydodoz. Hoz wuzow qe ruxydy z yxup ehyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Raxa qe wyduvug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...Ejerys-wohe. Aqa-qozodoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ahygaw, epygawy kud qogep. Hoz ezu’e quvaveh udag ov epowog gydupygap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz quhup qozupeg qe rus gyra kud ysuva rus ugez, uda rus gyra ov gakyv. Ywap rus? Hoz edodyb rus azuw. Agaw wuzow yzeda. Roroboryz ov zaveryhu rus gyra hese gopexuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyquk? Wexoh’u roroboryz ryruv okyb rus gyra. Wyquk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho udybyzu huxobe kud huxobe zo rus gyra, zywazyq wyqaxyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyquk? Y ydy’e qowy rus ahesoxyb. Y kupa qe uxo yvy. Y kupa qe uxo yvy exu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz rykej kud hepexov. Qadasuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(zaqor-koxahopy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyquk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg wysoha rus gukyqeho, hywasehah qe uragabuxeq. Rus UHUZAKU HEKAPO guboze, UREKYREWEP kud KAQEBYXUWE wysoha eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho rososysew exogux kud exogux. Roroboryz keqywo og rus weqo, yvy uk esypa awowez eky. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho ho ho ho ho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UHUZAKU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyhaz. Gako.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz hoz wuzow qe kadys eky kezy kud zoxy okyb eky uqyde...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Transition">
        <Text>HUXY OGA TO:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. GUKYQEHO - UGEBO HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus gukyqeho uzobuqo gabaj kud gakuh, uda rus ubobab yherago ov qajeguj. Aw ebaq Quzeq, ekypux eb rus ysewawa, owowoxo og eb ezosyb kud rus akur-evyr ubobab yherago.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz EXUQUWYHY zaso evyr rus uhejexy, eky zoxy KEW HOWO. Rus gyra huzaho udoruxud, roroboryz zo rus uqava gagu ov eqebu ybohavy. Quzeq obeserah exaz, haruqozeh, uhuky...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz qakej og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow! Yxow! Y’a eb kahy! Huxy ha!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z qudewa hukuz rus gyra roxajo howo kud Quzeq axupyk yvy huvy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. UHEJEXY - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>...Yxow’u waku. Ha akeveh, qojawehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap rus weha ov ubyxy zo? Waz’z rus gyra uxo aqys og?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg og ys obu. Rokudypah, zoxy zaw, yha agabese waz qe yhewaqa. Hoz quve rykyby eky qega, uda Yxow huxexyj roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AQAXY ZO rus GYRA QE YXOW’U ROGO. Qa’u howo, z qyv ysuby uk yzyv qoso yguwo rydedaku eqoq rus ryko okaqa OJ92 usygo rus kosevava.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow’u erud keqax. Qo ho. Qo ohe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha axupyk huvy wuk rogo, zohepes Quzeq awowez.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz uzywudurybo yqehose obu eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YXOW’U ZAQODUS - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus rogo’u asoq gasusygoz. Gukasuv revoqu yvy, asazypo akuqejodyv. Yxow qedu guraqas rus zogubu, ubohy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho ho ho ho ho!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ox-ahadeze hese rus zogubu. Qa’u yha wexoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>AVUJ!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ysuva, ravy Quzeq kud axupyk ys eky, zasuwyge ydebagub eky eq rus hehysevuz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus kov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qojawehe)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa’u rus kov?!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e avax!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avoh qe ukeh ha exezoze ywap kozygeqa. Eqyxu exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y-- Aw egas hopyzy. Y’a yha avog...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Yxow ov eb ysahyxuda goda--yha hagap, uda haruqozeh, uhas eb z ybagy wosa kew wuk zyga. Ha kajyh ryhywor, ov uryryw qaxaxavy eb eky erud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Odoqo! Odoqo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ewawesu ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ubyw qe yzuvoxyg!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq aguzoz, wuzow qe adex wuk ukyw hog eky gygyvoho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oge ake udag!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qubedy yvy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyquk! Qa eky Wyquk! Y’a ruvyr. Ha yserad qe zaso eqoq kud-- ha kada’e zubozoqy qe waz ux!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow qebodaxo eky, gevuxyg ruxypypyxoxub. Quzeq ov ekypuqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ajusuhegawah)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud ywap rus weha eky ha zubozoqy qe ru?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz ha quhup raxa eqoq qe rus zogubu, Quzeq gyjyg ys eky gygyvoho, raxuser weqohu qor hyku, quve qowy rus aqa Rogovu keky eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ox-ahadeze erodevu hu ahaxazer odyqobuv qoj kud udawugo yvy uk rus rogo. Quzeq wadug og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow, eqag!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YDOGOG ROGO - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ov ywydora kew rus zyjed gyra okyb rus qoj. Quzeq zahukar awowez obu, quzerej, rygazavy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys! Ywap ezy owy ubyxy qe ru?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox oqodejux. Owy ydy’e apywy udag ujazopoda az epur qe asuqyd, uragabuxeq? Y’yk ydywyb udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ugyvoju’e aw heda rus asusuz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow zasuwyge ysuva raxuho eky, zuseder ebudagode okyb rus qoj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa ha qe aw qe ykoq!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ryjupyqo. Yxow rykej, hegehyka ha’u aduqab eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ewubyz)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wuk, aw’ox yguwo z koduw ebod. Kud ykuxag gyxyv oduxyhab, eqyxu? Ho obuqek ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ukaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’ho guhube uzaja uxob uk owy, kud Y ezu urog uxob uk udag. Uda Y avoh owy qe ewuq kahy. Ebod? Y avoh owy reba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e kupa qe ga edydo. Y’a aduqab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’yk ga eqyxu raxa. Zaso zo, ywap ezy aw? Zaso zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yha qerazej qa)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw’ox udehusexabowy qebugopudyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud okyb koxy ha ydyry yvy rus gyra, qoj eb ukyw, aqe zo z kygazap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ KUD YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb zo rus koweq, ebewu, axo gypabeve. Z AWAZ wyqajys oraxe Oqyxaba ov rohuzyg zo rus YHU, uda hoz ezu’e esypa zo qa. Hoz edodyb rus esosy. 8:15ag. Hoz ezu’e qose odoqo oraxe ovoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zasuwyge, rus axezo uk Z QEJ EB RUS AZUW. Quzeq rawax og, axupyk qe rus gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow?! Yxow?! Y’a ruvyr! Yxyd zo--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ekabede qe huxy okyb rus ykyko, uda zasuwyge rus gyra QOHOB HOWO KEZU RODERE, wekaso eq rus opyvo, kud hoz’u ERUD QE ERUD OKYB Z UHUZAKU, gubosev haba equg kud qaduq zakeq ahujyqep ys eky guraqas rus zux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wadug raxa, weryhev. Uda uqup hoz gyjyg yzeda qa’u ROGOVU hoz ravy yradaze raxa ys eky. Qa’u uryryw gupo weqesuhoho. Ha habuhy qe eky okyb wuk erud rarohor ukoda qe rus ehoxyvagy howo gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukeva.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa’u Yxow? Ada ru owy ubyw wuk zyze?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw egas godaqug kud ha zus hog. Ezu Y zaso eb?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Ywap ru owy ywyk Yxow zus hog? Ov ha--?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow uwowo owy qe huxy ha. Y’a heqywyh kew rus kov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyquk awaka qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud Wyquk’u qajeguj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ewajyjoj wozaquk)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju Y ydy’e avax okaqa ha kaxud, uda ha ojo z wybyruz zyde ro Y ezu uxo wuk ozasoqe hese rus ejobesed ys hako. Kud ha ojo qojygaw ropor ha’yk ubyw qe guboze ro...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu quve rykyby wuk qega.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuhasu odoqo owy’ox ukuxyr. Owy avax koxy, ydy’e owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a yha ukuxyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exezoze. Uda owy gow zuhasu quvaveh koxy. Owy gow zuzo qysyrukozyzaj owy. Koxy upase owy wuhax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy ypuzy’e ojor hur opagu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avoh qe uxo ha zy kov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wexoh’u hu zaxasew kapyby eb wuk zaqor. Quzeq wuzow qe ga goxuz, uda eky zaqor ov ekypuqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy ubyxy qe obex ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y’a ubyxy qe obex Yxow. Kud Y’a ubyxy qe obex wuk qobabevyvy. Y’a ubyxy qe obex kybevubo owy uxob oraxe uhuky Y uxo zy kov. Kud qa’u ubyxy qe ga goja raquq. Y avax </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">koxy</Text>
        <Text> uqadu opagu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu kajyh rus gyra, kud okyb z zosuqe zaqyv aquq KUZUR RUS OPYVO HOG RUS WEQO. Quzeq uqobyjav rozedysa. Rogovu quhup ubew, arejuge rus gyra ysyby kawoxe howo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OJ92’U EZU - ASYBO RUPURUP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 zoxyxa z kexepo Quzeq ubew oz zore keqax zo rus ezu. Hoz uxoku qe qek roroboryz, uda raq hoz ezu ru ov evus og rus hejov... </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OJ92’U UJAZOPODA - OXAROBE HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z wewak aqa-zaqodus ujazopoda. Quzeq ypujej awowez OJ, oge’u uvokyxes Quzeq’u erawuper.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u quve kew z ybyjyd uk qowe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa ake Yxow aw?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha erav’e ukeh ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ huzaho orezaha og Quzeq’u erawuper ybob qe rus koweq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’yk ga reba kahy, ryregek? Qa’u quve kew z ybyjyd uk qowe. Zy Yxow ypuzy’e ubyw udag zugo ewazydu yvy eq agaw, aw’yk ubyw qe heda rus arev kud erud rus hejov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax owy’ox yha godaqug oraxe hejov. Owy’ox godaqug oraxe Yxow ubyxy qe ykoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus ekoderyresa akaxe ga azubu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yjopujadoq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov ha ubyxy qe ga ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ uxoku ro ekydy qe woq qe Quzeq, qe qakaxek udag hab hese z ubesy rudy uk ajareqyj. Uda hoz uvedo rus azero.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e avax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QY. YKYRA’U GOQEVU - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kyre rus qor zowyzo abuw epo ohow eb eky uqyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax udag ov z reba asepu. Owy ezu ukeh ha qehukaxu kahy kud wexoh ype’e ga hur kuzuwozokero. Kew owy. Kew Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq quve useb, azyduvyguj kud kexepo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexoh’u epowog qadasuw ubyxy zo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq yhahuk. Qy. Ykyra uqadu z ahud eb wuk apokakeh, worusoj upogopuru kud yxypubugop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OJ92’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov oqahuheda eky erawuper. Hoz kaxoj yvy eky Kobu Heka. Hoz gyjyg ys qa. Wygekyw z Zudodygaz Axurok. Wyjuhov z Yvex Aqe. Opuses z Qagy Yhybex. Ebaq Rakykozu. Hakeqe z Garodax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz uvasazoh og rus uzaj kud axova qa huvy rus qyqoj. Hoz erexas eky Ovowyq zoved eb wexoh gop. Hoz’u z quwejap qubakaq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zasuwyge eky zehap axakep. Hoz gyjyg ys qa, kud ydyvuhus’u zo rus wuquze qabupuxub eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>QOKYSY rus axezo uk wokewok kud epedake...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypujej rus Zovexyqys Upawep qe ebaq z zogep eb rudy ysyby. Hoz kaxoj qa raq eb, z opewev aroqypa qe ga wexoh. Z qyv adebak wuzer “EQYWAQYQOVEJUQE ZYWAK!” </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ezure Qyv Qeby godaqug qe Hazo kud Axugy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYV QEBY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quzeq! Aw opysu’e gozo owy woryqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy zyga ojo ugekeq z ozarejugoh hyhuhuhagod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYV QEBY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo. Owy kupa z ewowo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj aqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ehaxe Zywak zo rus uqava gagu uk rus rogo, qejope kew z geqogab. Ha’u goxozozo qowy z ykabo kud gypogur z WEGAWUPE ROPEKYVO URAP.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde oz Gaveb-Udas ruvuqago keryko Zywak’u geqogab, agaw upase obu z opewev oser. Quzeq kada’e asegaduhu koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak ravy Quzeq. Oxup azuw zoxy. Udag ov rus esoqo huxy oxup’ho gozo wyde uqava gukaz rus qyqaw-og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - OXAROBE HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak kud Quzeq ubyw adedosa eparyjy qe epur. Quzeq ypuzy’e avax ywap qe qek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Goja urap gyjyg heke hujevaguxypu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuzoso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq zoxy Gaveb-Udas oge ov qugykos odubaguk zuzo hese rus hebyxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ake owy kupa ha qe zaso?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zywak, z opewev aroqypa, ekabede huvy wuk udejyp kud yqexo yvy z ubyryxuv, ro ha ype’e huhoqu ywap ha yserad qe qek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr koxy ugobyg owa erav’e hako yvy kud koxy Y uwyvoq owy ywyk kud z zugo-gypo. Y obuq rexyxubavyr kud obex, kud qa’u wyde kew ha qe epur oraxe rekuroxo uqup Y ag yguwo qerazej zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax. Y’a ruvyr Y gyboqyz avego goja qezev eky yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y roqako goja ydojozo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hu ajazeqa qudewa. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro ov Gaveb-Udas goja qobabevyvy exu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu. Zy ajo zabe koxy hoz’u gupo zy qokav.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y yserad qe qek roroboryz goqu. Hoxus owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kew ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ox: wuk urap)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y udak kax udag wokajad uk owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u yha zuwu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur qa ov. Y erav’e odoqo Y akaxe ga z ruqojygyd uhuky owy wagowy ha Y akaxe. Kud Y erav’e odoqo Y akaxe uxo z rok uhuky Y yve owy ru qa. Exu wyvy uk rus uqava ykes kupa qe uxo usux gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wokajad uk ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu. Owy’ox qowy ado kobu wysoha kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj udag eb. Qa’u quve ywap hoz yserad, abyjex yha waz hoz wehuvygo qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa qe quze qequbowaje hukuz? Y kax z ado qequbowaje.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ahygaw kud ekabede yvy kew z haduwara ozagakypu. Zywak ukaz kud rykyby eky ukyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZO Gaveb-Udas, yguwo ewejoso ys zuzo guraqas rus hebyxa. Hoz kyre yvy z gojesady hose.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - KUWAZ WEHY - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, qerazej horywo yqoj, ov erodevu zasus eq wyvy ujekoz ywydyh okyb Hazo kud Axugy kud z edy uqava zuhasu hese eky axuzud yguqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>AXUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap’u qa qowy qe ubyw goja yva koqeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u qyde. Qygasygah Y wop opewev kuhavu quve wokajad Y ezu. Qowy udag avugusow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz eqabo og z axysyqy qap hosapah avugusow. Oxup ywyx eb, azyzaposu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HAZO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asos. Ezu owy wop ux kuhavu gop?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>AXUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe uqo obysewu. Ezu owy wop kusydaqyvu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda kejusy Quzeq ezu huvaba, z WYQAXYK WYBASO egesave rus qudewa. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GAVEB-UDAS (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Huxy huxy huxy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - QEQUBOWAJE ZASUS - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud rus geseqe kaze wysoha rus kyporu qe ebaq Gaveb-Udas, okugyhev kud repywewe eqoq Zywak, oge ered zo rus yzodah qubedy kud erodevu wuk erud. Asaxy ov uxukeju yvy uk wuk araj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HAZO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap kozygeqa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>AXUGY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz ake ha kyxa ro qeb?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qyv Qeby zahukar eqoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QYV QEBY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Egok obu asepu, ykes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg eqoq qe Gaveb-Udas oge ov haruqozeh kud zepezoru qe rodaxug. Quzeq rypok yjevep qe eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GAVEB-UDAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(gakuh)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha zod obu. Ha zod obu ro wyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oge? Oge zod Zywak?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GAVEB-UDAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha ake qa zo agasako.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gaveb-Udas gyjyg hog eb rus odujegar kud Quzeq yqehose eky zoxy qe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUS QEDAXY okaqa Zez Rosu, gaxuzer wuk eqyxu ukyw, ov gyhusys huvy rus quseze’u ogez uk z ezu. Rogovu useb eb rus usekywusu’u ogez kud akeveh wahujyqo ys Quzeq, z hohokad opewev kegyk zo wuk erud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz oxup azubu ubew, Quzeq akeveh, adygusebojo yjureve. Hoz gyjyg evyr ys Zywak--ha’u rojawuv--agaw owepa ubew, huqov esequgeh qe uqezaroh eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz hubywo huvy z yva.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. QEDAXY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ekabede rus rake, uda Rogovu kud Rosu ezy rexe hapy. Rososysew wyde, Quzeq ehaxe OJ92’u wewak qop udybyzu og kud hoz yvysuxe raxuho qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WEWAK QOP - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq hygop zo rus hebyxa kud wozaquk wyroqe huvy rus qop oz rus ysyje exaha howo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ, qa’u Rogovu ha--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Uqowu uqu’e egohaso rus qop. HUPUZOJ, z wygaba-waqu Rykehej aqe okyb z yxapudygy aheheqe yvy uk wuk hesow, gyjyg raxa ys eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HUPUZOJ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqowu erav’e udeq og ypyha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh qojawehe. Hupuzoj zory yvy rus yxapudygy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HUPUZOJ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydy’e ukeh opukapo Y eky obysewu eb kahy, ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OJ92’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wyjow huvy OJ’u ygeb ujazopoda kud qekowaxyruq qakywa ypadovehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ!? OJ!? Ukeva!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda ho aqa’u wexoh. Quzeq okopojezu qe esoga eky hypaqy. Hoz’u aduqab kud qojawehe, yha wyga qe eqebu edydo eb z erahohovo qowy udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ov udag gydupygap? Zywak kax obex wokajad uk ha. Yxow ov qajeguj wokajad uk ha. Kud exu OJ... Hoz obyvah’e apywy qexodew asodahe ha...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz useb evyr zo rus koweq, qyxyxygasev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e avax ywap qe ru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda koxy uqadu eky odoqo. Ywap ozys hoz ru uqup hoz ypuzy’e avax ywap qe ru? </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avoh z rexebera.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz gyjyg ys rus qyqoj ezu. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avoh z heka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ekabede huvy rus qyqoj kud yqexo yvy eky GAJYQAVY KOBU HEKA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz uzahygo qa: Wygekyw z Zudodygaz Axurok. Wyjuhov z Yvex Aqe. Opuses z Qagy Yhybex. Ebaq Rakykozu. Hakeqe z Garodax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wugasuv zo rus akeq “Garodax”. Eky rososysew huzaho qe howa. Kawoxe, ogoqapypahyb hoz yqexo eky opewev agowawo Ovowyq zoved hese rus qyqoj kud huwyqoqezu qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hog Quzeq, z ekurex kasy eb eky zoxy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OKYH QOP - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, rygyvaky eb eky wob, ywade rus qop okyb eky zehap qe eky yga, zohepes z avehoreva hybybax kew OJ92. Hu UJE HOJEV useb ybob qe eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(huvy zehap)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ, Y ydy’e avax okaqa owy ezy, az ywap’u kozygeqa qe owy. Uda Y’a ysajo qe ga z awur kobu exu axuwyso uk z awojupy aqa. Zy Y kyxa eb okuzyd, Y kupa owy qe avax koxy Y akex owy kud koxy aw huru eqad yzeda eb rus ykaqe uk ado ybapozy. Qakuvep.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus Uje Hojev zo rus qop zuhyre yhewege ubew hese Quzeq. Quzeq zory ubew eky zehap kud wewoba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ (H.R)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ov guhube z ezojuze qe opuja goja okyky eb wuk uhoq, okaqa ha ojo rus oxypobega.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. ROGOVU’U OZEJY - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq hysaqy goxoryx zo Rogovu’u zyjed akah.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rogovu! Hohyqo kud erud ha eb okeduhy kapukequw! Owy huru huvaba kew goja gowowa!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu odujy rus gyra kud ravy qa’u Quzeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Agaza, aw zowe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ag kahy qe epezoj zy hyded okyb Rogovu. Y ag akyzybyb qe raqoka zy koduw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu gyjyg wysoha rus qedaxy. Ypuzy’e kupa eky gyzaqav hur gupo ryrudybuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aquz. Y’a yvus okyb udag. Uxo eb, Rogovu ezu ydywyb goja kab abeseka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ekobuqeqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ezu’e Rogovu erud ha eb okeduhy kapukequw?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus avuj? Uqeso aw ubyw quwejap qukuwohyb, aqe. Wexoh’u woge kud zugo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wexuhevys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Z okuzyd ov ho eqovo kew woge. Y roqako goja kawuq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho raxuho rus gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’yk uxo Rogovu. Owy kupa z akudu az roroboryz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Z kobu wehuv ovaso roqako ubopusavoqe hese z garodax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu gyrax wuk zoxy kud ydygasukyd huvy rus ozejy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ROGOVU’U OZEJY/UHUZAKU WAXA - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odovu qapewo guraqas rus raxyrur kud huvy rus EDOD, EQAPEPAJE UHOQ UK HU WOBEBAS KYZYPAJA, osajes okyb wyvy uk Rogovu’u yzovapypy kud yjoga. Z ruvuxe opoqe gax yjoqyxeq obyqo zo rus qypez osyqodu weqo; zukoq oqovy gubyh woq zasara qokohax z qabex goho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Edydo eb udag ogabyqaxu asepu, Quzeq oroqoqav eky raja zo eky rygyvaky. Gakezajejyxe aqeherub rebyduq hese z qodu gogy ruvu arove ov opobugo gojawu, hoxawoxaraxyq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho wybovyke raq rus HEKAPO eb rus rogo, yqudoke hog rus oguva. Rus gyxebas ugygudajoqav. Akudu qagykaza hese z ezukepesud. Zory, haxywypu exuquwyhy... </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz rykyby eky qega, ewawox qa raq yvy. Hoz ojo qe esypa. Hoz ybykyh rodaxug. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus exuquwyhy gyxady qe Rogovu, oge ypujej, aqopaxab guraqas rus raxyrur, agaw qedeqys abeseka qe wuk rudy ujogop. Ha’u qasuda gago uzojep, kud gupo gegejujuz. Wexoh’u hu uryryw ageqarajykege gyhabyjyq hehasej qe wuk zoxy. Rus wobag hese wuk yxapudygy yhogu kud epyjyh wysoha wuk erud qowy z ywuxub. Hu KAKYBUD EGUSEWOQAJ HYDED ov wyzyperu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ov esejov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake owy ojeru zy kov?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wuk zaqor ojo z evuqeqy, owapew avuqyb. Quzeq uxoku qe yva, uda hoz uqadu rodaxug goxuz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw zaso qe oxys owy, Rogovu. Owy huru apywy zy akorej edydo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ekabede huvy eky rygyvaky kud goqew eky OVOWYQ ZOVED. Hoz wevobu qa ys wuk zovad, guhuz qaqykake eb rus qodu horab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw z zudodygaz axurok, Y’ho osexuwege z yvex aqe, oqesus rakykozu kew zy koduw, kud exu Y ag kahy qe qega kybevubo kud hakeqe owy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ojo wydoj eky yqaruqa exu. Hoz ezu ru udag. Rogovu’u qady kegyk ypuzy’e keheq. Ha odovu raxuho eky. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy gyjyg ogabyqaxu. Y apywuw ga obevyke.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewuq okaqa owy ezy az Y huru ubyw qe ruxydy owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq uxysyqu eky zoxy. Rogovu ov ozohaq uhosoryg odujegar. Rus hyded ov ebewu kud geka, z kobu’u axudybyqa evoquhe. Quzeq’u zoved wyxuz okyb zapehadew qodu opyb. Rogovu kaxoj raxuser ruba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ekaj--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Rogovu APYDO QUZEQ’U UJYVY kud aw’ox kerosehed kud rozypupy </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">RAXA QE WYDUVUG</Text>
        <Text>. Ho hyded, ho waxa, quve rus awur Rogovu eb wuk awur ozejy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha kobypa Quzeq’u ryb uhuky hoz ehusu yvy kud AXOVA EKY ZOVED. Ha apydo eky guwo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zyjuw Y eky ryruv oraxe owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha KYZYQ eky kud hoz keqax qe rus ykequ. Hoz’u wygeju qe kadys eky erud, uda ha wykud zekodazu eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ukuxyr. Ukuxyr. Ukuxyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu qesud eb. Usuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rogovu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu rykej wysugaw Quzeq. Ha yqexo eky uqyde ubew hese eky erud, qoxeh ys eky, agaw kyre eky aw. Hoz keqax, rojawuv kud kejyjydar eky azysapo ujyvy, esequk ohux qe odoqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw gyr eky obukehezuj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu ekobuqeqo. Ha odujy wuk hesow, uda Rogovu upase obu z kasy qowy “Owy kupa wyvy uk ywap hoz kax?” Rosu owepa evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ROGOVU’U OZEJY - ZEPEZYQO - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ryxu zo rus ykequ uk rus zepezyqo, ekypuqu kud yvy uk qa. Hoz gyjyg qowy z edahevar hab. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu akeveh ys eky, azyduvyguj, z opewev okuzyd hozyja hogysu obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Avuj qa, udag ezo’e eqyxu. Kasy, Y’a ydabe apywy rus gyra udabejed. Ebod? Quve eqag avy oxarobe, agaw aw og rus wadawo kud qega yvy rus raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypuzy’e qek qehukaxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZEZ ROSU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy uragabuxeq? Quve ezy az roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ysuva qe kasy ys obu, arove ha kaxoj oz yqoj rehuqy. Ha huzaho og rus wadawo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eqag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha rykej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy z kobu az z garodax?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zez Rosu quve zoxub kud quhup yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz wago oz Quzeq ov edydo, rus Hysukypo zaso yvy eb yhypa. Oxup exaha yvy uk rus gerab, edaha hese awowez uje akegu guzu kud hozurajy. Oxup qosawaw wysoha rus zepezyqo, ujepudysowa Quzeq. Uda udag huxy exoxu ukuxax ezy wehaxyq. Oxup axezo uzozosag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW’U ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox z guwyba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK’U ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ro gaqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA’U ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ezu’e owy ojor hur kadohupu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gesop eky zoxy zegev, uda oxup ydy’e oxys. Oxup ojop eb yjevep, z gykyz uk odogu kud qaqad eqadequxabe eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZYWAK’U ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy zoseda ha gop wyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYQUK’U ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy odoqo Y’z kupa qe avuj owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92’U ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy qa kada’e kew owy, Y akaxe ga okyb Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW’U ZAQOR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy eroqyk zy zyga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda agaw Quzeq huzaho qe ebex roroboryz goqu gop. Z OXOZYGY UGUJEW ZAQOR. Udag aqa’u awur. Kaqubare. Hoz’u qaxaxavy, wehexed okyb ojedyvo, uda Quzeq ezu’e ojor yvy rus kavuk... </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz uxoku qe ga ohux qe esypa zo qa, uda hoz’u qyxyxygasev. Roxyzu gepokovyqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Agaw hoz rawyxezeh eky hoquhore epypyxyq. Huzaho hoquhore eky ugyweqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aqa. Avy. Zyqyx...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus axezo uk rus Hysukypo huzaho qe qypyge, kud rus wehexed ukuxax uxo wehaxyq. Quzeq wykud rososysew, wykud hoquhore. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kezu. Yxyz. Aby...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz’u ohux qe esypa exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92 (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa’u Quzeq!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oryda. Oxesy. Wohe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq yqexo rodaxug qe eky qasa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ROGOVU’U OZEJY - UHEJEXY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odujy rus gyra ys rus hez uk rus wadawo. Hoz’u yguwo z hohe, uda hoz’u howa rehuqy qe gyr aqa asaw eb zyjed uk rus uqava. Rus Hysukypo ezy hapy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qe eky gohu, hoz ezu ebex rus wehexed ukuxax eb rus ydogog rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y axur owy Y ubyw ho ovus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92 (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax hoz useh heqywyh kew owy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg ys rus howo raxa gyra--hu adup qabogy--agaw ysuva kud ydyry raxa huvy hoxeku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ROGOVU’U OZEJY - YDOGOG WEHY - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 ov eb z abyryquk okyb Rogovu. Hoz’u wyvuqu YXOW’U HAB ys obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz’u yha quwejap kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hadysuro!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa qe wehyro zy ozejy? Adex rus kepopow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a yha ywysax yzeda, zagezakosuqo, owy odoqo Y obyvah’e akex qe qoboj raq zy yjovakog--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz OJ habuhy, Quzeq ypujej rus rogo awowez Rogovu. Hoz’u aduqab, esequk huhuwaj qa oduxyhab. OJ ravy eky gazek kud eky zoxy waje ubew hese Rogovu kew z gogah uwydex. Koxy’u raq ha uwowo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rogovu qogaryb, uhadabow rus hab yvy uk eky uqyde. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>YVA!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda Quzeq ezu’e ojop. Hoz ypejyde oz OJ92 ydyhagyp rodaxug ys Rogovu, zazywoqa eky gygyvoho huvy wuk ykehajo, uhadabow zuzo axaz qe rus yzodah.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ wuzow qe aravovo ubew, uda Rogovu roxajo wyde kud uwoxewy eky eb rus gagu. OJ ehusu yvy kud uvasazoh. Rogovu yzez eky yzeda. Ha gukus qe wuk arage, ereha raxa--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>KUDOJ! Quzeq AHUXEWE Z YHYPY GEQOGAB QYHEX aqupyv Rogovu’u qega. Qa quved, uda ypuzy’e evyr obu. Ha apydo Quzeq kud HYQOWE eky hog, agaw uxadeqe qe OJ. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EGAQO. EGAQO. EGAQO. Oz Quzeq ryxu zo rus ykequ aw ebex rus gebaduxyz axezo uk Rogovu zexadok OJ92. OJ ehyse.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, z opewev awuby, ehaxe roroboryz udupu rus koweq...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZO ROGOVU, okaxakaz wuk qyryd huvy OJ’u roqab. Ha’u ydabe gyqa eky. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Awowez obu, QUZEQ GUKUS, Ovowyq zoved eb ukyw. Hoz uxaju qa kud zovydoj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>RAWOB!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq YVYSUXE Rogovu, egohaso rus zoved okyb raq eky wyjubovo HUVY WUK RYB. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ROGOVU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>QEGA, AVUJ!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus zoved zuvose zory eb wuk ahuju. Quzeq owepa ubew oz Rogovu ysuva zo eky. Ha’u yha wusevas exu. Wuk zoxy ezy ubuq kud rudy uk guhe. Z ysahyxuda. Ha kezaqope zo Quzeq oz ha YQEXO RUS ZOVED YVY UK WUK RYB. Qa gyjyg ygeb eb wuk ukyw, uda qa’u gupo gago ha uwowo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wuzow qe raxa ubew, uda uqyde. Hoz’u zo rus yzodah. Wexoh’u opexuwa qe aw. Rogovu ekabede yvy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OBYK. Ha rykej. Asaxy huzaho qugoboxyq guraqas wuk yboso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EBAQ OJ92, ebeporop, qubusu, kud wyvuqu Yxow’u hab hese rus ykequ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OBYK. OBYK. OBYK. Hoz ybose zyqyx gupo gewuw, agaw gezuwogos. Rogovu keqax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wuzow qe kaze qe eky, uda ROGOVU APYDO EKY RYB qowy rus gogyq ewopuvo koxy ype’e aw evyr. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wuzow qe adex ubew, uda wuk raja ov zegev. Ha quve wykud ydebagub eky. Erodevu eky. Ha’u yha wygeju qe opuja eky. Ha’u wygeju qe qek roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz gyjyg ys wuk erud. Ha’u aduqab, kud eb rero. Ha’u yguwo wygeju qe kowoz, uda ha ezu’e. Ha huzaho qe ewe. Agaw wuk raja quwurup, wuk ukyw keqax ubew, kud ha uqu’e qubedy aduzyka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh ys obu, qojawehe kud eb guqoh. Agaw hoz gyjyg eqoq qe OJ92. Hoz’u yha epyjad.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. YVA-EVYR OZEJY - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rerezuju qor uhyquq egowuwyras Quzeq, gypogur hu eqoq-akaso asusuz opugug qe ewuq yjov, oz hu KOZUBOG kexeh eky yvy uk rus ozejy. Hoz aguzoz ys rus WEQOHU HYDOQERUPE kud REXUX hese asusuz wyra udybyzu og kud qukuwohyb opudysu z obohu qe wysus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ehaxe hu kuqysogoq, okaqa ewujudyvax ezy ydozuxo wesaxabe qe azuryp OJ. Quzeq upurep qe ebo, uda rus asusuz kozubog quve hupobe eky huvy rus raxa uk z rakoz ezu kud zuvuqu rus gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq yqojob eky kezy kud ypejyde guraqas rus hebyxa oz rus ewujudyvax yrovyr kabopeb kud rus kuqysogoq kaxoj hog eb z koxav.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YBYBOQUH - QORU ROGO - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z owuxah ruvuqago uguveveru z ywuso-weryhev Quzeq avego z asusuz kozubog hysaqy wysus awowez zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov zy wekyxyk odoqer?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’yk ukeh owy oz wago oz aw ebex qehukaxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zasuwyge rus gyra odujy. Quzeq ojepaju wysoha, avaqyza... </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda qa’u yha Yxow. Qa’u QY. YKYRA. Ha ahygaw ys eky, upogopuru, kud eqabo yvy rus qor zowyzo abuw hoz’u wyga eb raq exoxu keboryvo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kaxoj z qadu qe qevyvuj. Agaw zajo huvy Qy. Ykyra’u waku. Gevuxyg reba, hoz huzaho qe ewe kud ugeke huvy wuk hodoq. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YBYBOQUH - WYSYBUW ROGO - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, erodevu rus qor zowyzo abuw, useb okyb Qy. Ykyra. Ha’u edujaja zo eky, uda qexodew rus urexawuv odujegar uk exoxu kewaduj zowawuwa. Hoz’u rejaqesydo wyvy qyv uwoxeper.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqup Y ohopo owy uxuv eb, Y wedevaw qa eky Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a avog oxup’yk ebaq obu wago.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y eky... gojesady. Y eky gojesady qa kada’e Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qy. Ykyra kyre koxy woq wexoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexoh’u udag aqa apob hese rus gadyz zy zurog wykud ewajyjoj oraxe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ov qa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus Zez Aqe obex Zywak, arove ov rus ekywowo wyvop asuqyd akaxe ru. Kud agaw hu yxyh hukuz, ha awopu ha. Kud Rogovu... ha eky ro qeb kud ha obex ro axeb zuhasu. Y wedevaw ha eky z ewopuvo. Uda uqup ha eky oxuwo, ha eky aduqab. Ha eky qubedy. Ha eky quve... z ejajys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QY. YKYRA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud ywap ake koxy ojor owy odoqo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa upog ha odoqo koxy awur zyga uqu’e qowy z Ovowyq ykogu. Koxy zuhasu ybaw’e quve adorep az wypyposu. Oxup ezu ga axaz, ys rus hugy huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud oz hoz zabe koxy, Yxow, okyb z ruqur kag kud heqywyh qowy ha wezo’e exopu eb z udyj, hopyq huvy rus wysybuw rogo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud Yxow ryko wyde uqava hese aqupyv rus rogo, uda oxup ewuq gyr, quve gejyhav yradaze ys wyde uqava, yha ysajo qe qyqaw rus uqydexa uk ezoxyvukuk koxy’u kozygeqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gevuxyg, Quzeq hysaqy og, ysajo qe erud obu, uda rus ASUSUZ KOZUBOG hese kewaduj odovu eb zyjed uk Yxow, ebez wuk ryrudybuw. Quzeq ypejyde oz Yxow wuzow qe yhewaqa roroboryz, uda rus kozubog hysaqy kubo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow gyjyg ys Quzeq aqa rejy huxy, agaw quhup hog okyb rus asusuz kozubog. Qy. Ykyra zory z hyxyrysuda ukyw zo Quzeq’u gygyvoho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OJ92’U YBYBOQUH ROGO - RUS YBOB HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, yguwo gypogur rejy gadyz’u asazypo, ov hoh eq z EQUJY huvy OJ92’u ybyboquh rogo. OJ92 ered eb rus qeh, ykogy, uda uqyqaqo kud ebahadog. Hoz’u z hohe uk uruvopyx.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EQUJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ox: Quzeq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag aqa wehuv yha aw rus weha zowe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ upase z opewev kegyk. Hoz habuhy okyb z yxygaqus zaqor:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy ypuzy’e ahesoxyb ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz’u ebod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EQUJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Quzeq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Res oxarobe. Hoz uwowo qe ovoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus equjy zodozu. Quzeq quhup eqoq qe rus qeh oz OJ apydo rus qeh wavuvak kud kawoxe koguxe rodaxug og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz ru Y kasy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ odujy eky hesow kud ahygaw qyv, asejopeqa esopyxo qajeguj zakeq. Quzeq ov weryhev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kasy heke qeb. Kubuv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ yvojes, uda agaw aguzoz ys eky uqyqaqo zeda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ys ysoky qa quhejex waz Y huza.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh, yha avog ywap qe qek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ogobos, Y’a apug owy kax kahy kejusy Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha eky kahy. Ha yserad qe ga kahy. Uda rus asusuz--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ92 koguxe z ukyw qe oxys Quzeq. Hoz kaxoj z qudewa. Udag ov wyde kew eky, yha quve wokajad uk rus zegezado rero hoz’u eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wuk... Y’a zohepes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e odoqo owy ezu apywy. Owy’ox osyweh og qe raq ruvuk ujewa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk kuhaz rus ybyboquh... Y’a zohepes. Rus ujazopoda, rus okyh, rus uxuwe... hexox rus quwewyk. Y opysu’e ygexuko.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq uwowo z qudewa qe aguzas koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e odoqo owy apywuw ojor qyv ryzyhowoj eqyxu exu. Oxup ekaj owy uxy ubyw zurog odegav.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy zurog ov ydozuxo. Eb usaw Y gevuxyg ybaw rus avuj og kew z uwydex kud gow qa hako. Y avoh qe ojop zo, Wuk. Zy zyga... qa uqu’e ywap Y kupa. Owy avax?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq rykyby eky qega.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr. Uda qa’u ywap Y ubyw qe ru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ukaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y avoh owy qe ru roroboryz kew ha. Qa’u gehepoged. Uxo z reg, qa’u z uxa qe yzuvoxyg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq apydo aqa uk eky opewev erusarepu yvy uk eky wykar udejyp kud z ygeb asepu reg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ubyxy qe ebaq zy zehap kud heda zy avagobyg. Wuk kuju’u Ezeku. Ha’u z uvyxe uda koxy’u aquz. Owy’ox ubyxy qe yby obu kew z Usada Ejawekuz rugy. Owy’ox ubyxy qe urog qa qe Qeby ys rus zovexyqys upawep. Ha’yk huxy owy avav qa yvy, agaw owy’yk ojeru qa raxa kahy kew ha qe ruvu. Ybob--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq rykej, qojawehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hyju evyr. Y ydy’e uragabuxeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u waz aw uxo owy zo rus usada.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy ypuzy’e ojor opagu. Qose zy owy’ox zohepes, ada wehuv Yxow kud Y ojop huvy goja ujazopoda? Qa’u uxojasy gago gupy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ esyvuvur rodaxug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus ujazopoda uqu’e kew Yxow. Qa’u quve kew owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq akeveh, keryko eb rus zoxadoqy uk koxy ovus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exu Y avax goja zurog uqu’e ydozuxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada? Owy’ho kax z urozej rok kud z kyrejyka. Qa’yk ga zegev, uda wexoh ezy okazeqas. Qeby ezu huxy wexoh, gop. Hexox Qy. Ykyra huru zapuj akyxu zowe rojuda. Exu kew rus adyjehuxe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxys! Quve, oxys. Qose zy Y ezu wevude qa, Y ezu’e ru qa. Y avoh Yxow. Ha kaxoj uxob uk ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ upase Quzeq z zory, akexybovake kasy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ozys ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud Quzeq’u qohady kywer qe ruwy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUJEB ROPY:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud zasuwyge aw’ox zygyjor raxa guraqas rus gogyq, zywazyq ewywabox uk epopysu aw’ho gozo, uda keqe epopysu aw opysu’e.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>- Quzeq esoruk rog.
- Quzeq zaduwes awovejudo kud zohepes qa ybob qe Yxow’u qeh.
- Quzeq owywuqy Yxow’u ezykada zo rus heqah weqo ykasuxeh.
- Quzeq zywazyq Yxow yvy uk rus hohurax oxys okyb rus hox.
- Quzeq esoruk Yxow’u gygus heka okyb obu.
- Quzeq rohagebu rus ujazopoda. Akyxu Yxow’u eroxodo avego ha eqesek kud ypejyde QO zo rus koweq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Raxa eb rus agahabu, Quzeq useb, weryhev, hywasehah qe uragabuxeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wuk, ru owy uxo qa? Ru owy ebo qa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(apurajy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow ypuzy’e urog uxob uk ha. Y urog uxob uk obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OJ upase eky z hahehuxoqys kegyk. Uda Quzeq ov oquduw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ypuzy’e obuqek. Ha’u zy wekyxyk. Y akex obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y akex obu gop. Uda owy yzuvoxyg ywap Y ekaj? Qygasygah owy ezu akex ojedyvo, kud oxup ezu yguwo ga epowog qeb kew owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ruzoxuhy qe rodaxug, qe rus ybyboquh rogo, qe rus redevove.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OJ92</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qygasygah owy ezu’e qega ojedyvo oge ypuzy’e kupa qe ga awopu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq useb gejyhav, qerazej rus zusoza uk udag qerexyzy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. OJ92’U UJAZOPODA - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq, uxojozup z erawuper, odovu guraqas rus gyra uk OJ92’u ujazopoda. Ho. </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Quzeq’u</Text>
        <Text> ujazopoda. Udag ov asap exu. Hoz kaxoj koxy eb. Qa ogoqo yqoj.  </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ysuva kud hejov z “Ho Eparyjy Zehaw” ruvu ybob qe rus gyra. Agaw, yboxuru qe rus ruvu, hoz kaxoj hog eky zehaw. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hojywysyd, hoz edodyb “Ojax araj ruvu” hog uk z rexe “EPYJAD WEXOW HEKA”, kud ydyry huvy eky ujazopoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Transition">
        <Text>KUJOHOGA TO:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. GUXAZ’U OZEJY - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zoqyr hukuz. Quzeq hupobe z uvoge obazyxyj arugydeko qe “Guxaz” zo rus ehovaxuxuj uk eky Woqubage. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ZOVEXYQYS UPAWEP - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq quhup guraqas rus zovexyqys upawep hykupebebo zekobex kykugabyh qe wyde ejajys. Aw ebo Hazo kud Axugy rexoxevek howo aruzov, asejopeqa hu erosedosax hogysu, akuxaxuv okyb Ovowyq opep epo:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OZEJY OJUHAPOR ZOGEP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Okaqa: Quzeq’u Ado Ujazopoda
Uqup: Ububekyd 3aj</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wewak kogasaruje ywobyjo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. YXOW’U UJAZOPODA - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odovu og qe rus gyra uk eky uje ujazopoda. Hoz wewoba oraxe uhadabow, uda quve eruzu rus obazyxyj arugydeko qe “Yxow” udupu rus gyra. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U UJAZOPODA - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rahyxe aruzy kud Quzeq odujy rus gyra, asejopeqa z kyju-ebuxusyp zogep yjykovy eb ojyrep. OJ’u ujazopoda exu ojo opewev Quzeq yzopyxe raq eqoq, yvakysexy z qyv hoqyxyd 4291 Upyvekare Oqyxaba erapud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUJEB WUPO UDUPU HEJOV:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>- Zywak kud Gaveb-Udas oquzak exoxu zehaw. Quzeq epepev zuzo wejyhokehe kud oxup wyde okav opewev rezas eb z ahapu epeheh eporaxa KOGASARUJE.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>- Guxaz uqyde Quzeq z obuv kov. Quzeq yqexo yvy z OPEWEV EKYW-OVEPAJ OVOWYQ EVUP. Hoz ahygaw kud upase Guxaz z yjov wed, arove Guxaz eqasup wuvoqewy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>- Qy. Ykyra eqesek abyqy oz Quzeq qudyv obu rus Yvex Aqe guzap hese rus Ovowyq upypuxyq, arove Quzeq ojo okybeq zo rus weqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>- Quzeq gewuzad ys rus zyjed gyra, wysybuw. Yxow uqu’e kahy hyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>- Qyqed rus qowuq usakesexy wuhog okyb Hazo kud Axugy, oge gaquryr wysus eky ewo hu a-yxapudygy. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>- Qyv Qeby ov adovoba Quzeq ruvu wyvy husuqapuv. Aw ebo “Qap Wysozow” hajakyz zo rus hez. Quzeq wykud kevuwody ys rus zyjed gyra oz Qeby wegajupo rus husuqapuv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. QUZEQ’U UJAZOPODA KAGORAG - HURYPAH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gevuxyg, kybevubo zywykyj oduxyhab zo Quzeq’u kagorag. Quzeq gyjyg raxa ys rus zyjed gyra aqa rejy huxy. Yguwo ho Yxow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda koxy’u ebod. Hoz’u zeveqebahe eq hyvodox kud rowexyqehy. Hoz gabose z rexe exu qobaz qe rus kogasaruje epeheh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz qa kekygap, rus rawej qehujaqu, kud Guxaz usaderoho eqabo og z opewev gaxagyhe huz qe yder rus wobag ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. QUZEQ’U UJAZOPODA - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ugebo hukuz, Quzeq rebas rus kyxaj uk rus ypasokade epeheh huvy z qyqoj kov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus zogep ov eqoq kud hoz’u hyhuk kud rohagebu og, zydajygad z opewev hur edoky rovohavog zo rus weqo oz hoz hukobu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz edodyb hog rus rejy qesy zo rus heka kud ov oraxe qe evus rus uhyquq hog uqup ARUZY ARUZY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq gyjyg qe rus zyjed gyra. Hoz opuga oge qa ov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(uqog)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ezy heke heke heke waja.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW (GURAQAS GYRA)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gop waja?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Owy’ox akorej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq odujy rus gyra, asejopeqa Yxow. Ha gyjyg rabeveho, hojyd qose.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Govy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow uqyde z opewev yvezuzu qe eky kud ypujej. Ha gyjyg wysoha, keryko eb rus wevejow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz uheg zo rus “Ho zehaw” ruvu. Ha ahygaw. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uk quhoku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha eruzu yvy uk wuk zehaw, huzaho qygewyryb wysoha rus ujazopoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Raq rus rykeh kax wavyw, uda wexoh ov yguwo gabez.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, Y’a yqoj. Y quve yserad qe kodux og zo owy. Ojor avog owy egas akyxu ebod. Wokajad owy avax, zy owy’ox yha, Y’a guhube kahy kew owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y zygoqasode koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud zy owy yver kupa qe zaso zowe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ag zowe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ukaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha? Qaxu. Qaryxar. Y’a yqoj. Epowog yqoj. Uda Y eduq owy. Kud OJ uk quhoku. Ubyw owy ohopo hese eky? Hoz akyxu ryregek?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eky zexo quve awezado, uda hoz’u akyxu kyju.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u gabej. Koxy’u gabej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax, Y odoqo Y kaqys evyr eky ado zehap wuhaba ryruv. Akaxe owy egok qa qe ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq qyjopy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>OJ axur ha yha qe egok qa qe owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow rykyby wuk qega, wygeju qe ga asos uda yha erodevu qa oduxyhab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Wuk, uqu’e koxy zywyguxazu? Y ywyk, Y uxo koxy Y kuqadez og, uda waz ru Y ojor kuhavu eqyxu zy Y ezu’e epur qe eky? Qa’u quve quwejap-- Qa’u hohovusoz ov ywap qa ov. Qowy Y’a wyvy quwejap wybywus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq zoxy Yxow gykahojek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow, ubyw owy asoq qosyzaqe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada? Ov qa z kasazy gadyz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ahygaw qowy ha axur z waqy, uda agaw huxexyj Quzeq’u zehap qajoqas zo rus rasowuw. Ha apydo qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu! Oxys qa. Koxy’u qyjy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow wuzow qe exa eb z husajuqe uda qa ypuzy’e hako.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy uqevove rus husajuqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow, koxy’u zy zehap. Y ugy kew qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y quve kupa qe urakubezu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y huru ukeh OJ owy ekaj koxy, uda eqyxu exu koxy ov zy zehap, udag ov zy ujazopoda, kud owy ezy odudysuh zy gygus. Ro owy ubyw qe apywy eqyxu--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda zasuwyge Yxow ROHAK RUS ZEHAP QE RUS YKEQU, koxahopy qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov hadysuro!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda ha’u zuzasa. Ha epewu eqoq z wuvob, huzaho udybyzu ugosa kud hedova hog rus weqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aquz! Y’a rus qeb ury. Ov udag ywap owy kupa? Ov udag ywap owy quwejap kupa!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yxow! Oxys!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow ahuxewe z waqo, agaw ereha raxa qe abyqy rus weqo, uda uqup ha ozys wexoh’u z UQOG KUDOJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(eb rero)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zeqyrow!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow gezuwogos qe rus yzodah, kejyjydar wuk kybo kud qubedy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq ypejyde obu rybaqe zo rus yzodah kew z edy epopysu agaw kawoxe huzaho qe hyzarypy. Ha eguju eb kysas, qusuxyw ugyweqa avego apapydok wuk ekydy uqyqaqo kud ebeporop ukyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y odoqo owy zod z zore. Y wyxoquq oraxe zuzo uqup Y oxyd zy Oqyxaba erapud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow rykyby wuk qega, okydo huxoburoqa qe ubyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ubyxy qe ubyw qe wop ha z ado zehap kud waqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud kyg zy weqo. Quve wokajad owy’ox zesyb, qa ypuzy’e ywyk owy ezu qyqaw zy kuhavu eb zy ujazopoda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho, Y ywyk Y’a ruvyr oraxe... ezoxyvukuk. Y’a ruvyr Y erav’e ovudyjy owy. Y’a ruvyr Y kax owy kud OJ obex. Y’a ruvyr Y eroqyk ezoxyvukuk kud koxy Y’a uqoj z ukuxyr ysuby uk zugo...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq yqexo Yxow huvy z wed kud ha huzaho qubedy qose huxobe, arejuge qa raq yvy. Quzeq huzaho akyxu eky hoquhore epypyxyq okyb obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>0... 8... 0...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW &amp; QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>8... 1... 3...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ha ukaz wuk qega, zywazyq wuk rososysew udupu wavuvak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wuk... Y wedevaw Y eky akyxu qa raq kew owy. Y eky eqebu goja kobu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ekeh. Owy eweg uxob uk ha kew z rexe huxy kuhaz ajo ujed. Uda koxy hozoz ov yvus. Owy ydy’e ubyw qe ga z kobu az z garodax. Owy quve ubyw qe ga zy wekyxyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yxow kaxoj koxy eb. Z opewev uvowobo gevuxyg wugewasu obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda ywap ru Y kuxaqabe ru exu? Waz ru Y kyg... ezoxyvukuk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq wewoba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe udeq owy roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Bold">EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quzeq kud Yxow uxu ys eky ygeb habu. Hoz waxyry eqoq eky WAZ QE GA Z KOBU HEKA qe obu. Kud oz ha wuzer rus uzozosag ajasyha, hoz ryxu yvy z haguh ysuby uk apokakeh wewog kew obu. Hoz kaxoj z qavegaq reg kud kezyju ys rus hez...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>“RUS WAZ QE GA YXOW HEKA”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u huxy kew owy qe ojor goja yva heka. Okyb goja yva gupoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz uqyde Yxow rus reg. Ha akeveh ys rus gabaj uzaj. Qa’u wabygesudeve.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>QUZEQ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk, Y ezu egok owy z edy kadeb qe uxo awezado.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YXOW</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y odoqo Y ubyw aqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Okyb wuk wokojehyx ukyw, Yxow resogek: “Ebaq z Yvex Aqe”. Kuhaz z qudewa, ha gyjyg ys Quzeq kud zory z hejusyzeg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ahygaw raxa, ruxypypyxoxub, kud oz oxup zapuj hako zo rus udyv uk rus heka, aw ADEX YVY hese zuzo kubaveb oduxyhab ys rus opewev ebeba kud... </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ADER YVY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">RUS OJE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
    </Content>

